NK008(nya)001:2191: kun gzhi ni sbyor ba'i yum be ta li ni /
NK008(nya)001:2193: de dang gnyis su med pas na byang chub sems te thugs mchog ma ru rtse ste /
NK008(nya)001:2194: tshe'i rang bzhin thugs kyi sprul pa khro bo kun+da li'o //
NK008(nya)001:2195: tshe yi srung ma bzhi ni /
NK008(nya)001:2196: 'khor bud+d+ha bzhi dang ldan pa'i phyir gshed bzhi'o //
NK008(nya)001:2197: de yang bum pa ltar snang ba chos kyi sku la /
NK008(nya)001:2198: gzungs thag byang chub sems kyi rgyun lam /
NK008(nya)001:2199: de la spro bsdu byang ba ye shes kyi smon lam /
NK008(nya)001:2207: bcom ldan mgon po tshe dpag med //
NK008(nya)001:2208: chos nyid kyi skal ba byang chub kyi sems bskyed
NK008(nya)001:2209: pa chos nyid kyi tshe sbas pa'i don dus su
NK008(nya)001:2210: rgyal bas kyang bzung du med pa'o //
NK008(nya)001:2211: sems can gyi tshe chos nyid la rgyal po zhes bya'o //
NK008(nya)001:2212: wa te a pa ri mi ta +aa yur+dz+nyana /
NK008(nya)001:2213: chos kyi tshe ye shes dang ldan pa /
NK008(nya)001:2214: su bi ni sh+tsish+ta te dz+wo r+aa dza ya /
NK008(nya)001:2217: de bzhin du byang chub sems su bstan /
NK008(nya)001:2218: +amo sarba sam s+k+aa ra pa ri shud+d+ha d+harma te /
NK008(nya)001:2219: ga ga na sa mut+ga te swab+h+aa wa chags par
NK008(nya)001:2220: gyur cig pos srid pa gsum dang sems can gyi
NK008(nya)001:2221: bag / bi shud+d+he ma h+aa na ya pa ri wa re s+w+aah+aa /
NK008(nya)001:2223: bsnyen pa'i dus na ya m+aan+ta ka sku mdog dkar po zhi ba'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa /
NK008(nya)001:2224: phyag g.yas pa na dngul g.yon skyabs sbyin gyi phyag rgya'o //
NK008(nya)001:2226: sems thams cad ma lus pa'i nyes skyon /
NK008(nya)001:2227: kyi bag chags 'khru bar 'di skor la tshig mtshams
NK008(nya)001:2228: mi 'grigs pa mang du snang bas thag chod pa
NK008(nya)001:2231: de nas sbyar ba'i nye bsnyen dang sgrub pa'i skabs rnams chad snang /
NK008(nya)001:2234: zhing bcu bsgral ba'i sha khrag rus pas brgyan //
NK008(nya)001:2235: le brgan dar gyi cod pan du mas mdzes //
NK008(nya)001:2236: phyi nang gsang ba'i rten rdzas sna tshogs bshams la /
NK008(nya)001:2238: bdud rtsi sman gyi mchod pa rgya mtshor 'khyil //
NK008(nya)001:2239: rak+ta khrag gi rba klong 'khyil ba dis //
NK008(nya)001:2240: sgrol ging dmar po 'khor bcas thugs dam bskang //
NK008(nya)001:2241: dam tshig nyams chag thams cad skong gyur cig /
NK008(nya)001:2242: rnal 'byor bdag gi dpal dang sdong grogs mdzod //
NK008(nya)001:2243: dgra srog gcod pa'i phyag na ral gri dang //
NK008(nya)001:2244: dgra dpung 'joms pa'i ru mtshon dmar po dang //
NK008(nya)001:2245: bswe khrab bswe rmog bswe phub dmar po dang //
NK008(nya)001:2246: thabs shes mda' bzhu sag thag dmar po sogs //
NK008(nya)001:2247: dgra lha'i rgyal po dmag la chas ba'i tshe //
NK008(nya)001:2248: nye bar mkho ba'i go mtshon sna tshogs kyis //
NK008(nya)001:2249: sgrol ging dmar po 'khor bcas thugs dam bskang //
NK008(nya)001:2250: dam tshig nyams chag thams cad skong gyur cig /
NK008(nya)001:2251: rnal 'byor bdag gi dpal dang sdong grogs mdzod //
NK008(nya)001:2252: mkha' lding rgyal po shang shang sil snyan 'khrol //
NK008(nya)001:2253: mi dmar bswe yi bya khra ca co sgrog /
NK008(nya)001:2254: gtum chen dur bya 'ug pa'i rkan sgra bsdeb //
NK008(nya)001:2255: srin bya 'jigs pa'i gad mo chem chem sgroog /
NK008(nya)001:2256: mi bsrun mtshan mor rgyu ba 'byung po'i bya //
NK008(nya)001:2257: glo bur mi skad smra ba grangs med kyis //
NK008(nya)001:2258: sgrol ging dmar po 'khor bcas thugs dam bskang //
NK008(nya)001:2259: dam tshig nyams chag thams cad skong gyur cig /
NK008(nya)001:2260: rnal 'byor bdag gi dpal dang sdong grogs mdzod //
NK008(nya)001:2261: mtshal mdog nyi ma'i 'od 'phro zla ba'i mdog /
NK008(nya)001:2262: dmar ser li khri'i mdangs ldan rnga rngog 'phyar //
NK008(nya)001:2263: dmar nag me lce'i phreng ba'i zhing chen la //
NK008(nya)001:2264: sga dmar rin chen bdun ldan chas kyis mdzes //
NK008(nya)001:2265: cang shes sprin gyi shugs 'chang can gyi rta //
NK008(nya)001:2266: yid 'ong rgyan gyis mdzes pa grangs med kyis //
NK008(nya)001:2267: sgrol ging dmar po 'khor bcas thugs dam bskang //
NK008(nya)001:2268: dam tshig nyams chag thams cad skong gyur cig /
NK008(nya)001:2269: rnal 'byor bdag gi dpal dang sdong grogs mdzod //
NK008(nya)001:2270: zangs ri ltar dmar 'gying ba'i g.yag rgod ni //
NK008(nya)001:2271: byang sprin dmar po'i mdog can rtsi da pa'i zhol //
NK008(nya)001:2272: me rlung 'tshub cing 'khyil 'dra'i rnga ma g.yo //
NK008(nya)001:2273: stong gsum g.yo bar byed pa'i gom stabs can //
NK008(nya)001:2274: ngar skad 'brug ltar sgrogs pa grangs med kyis //
NK008(nya)001:2275: sgrol ging dmar po 'khor bcas thugs dam bskang //
NK008(nya)001:2276: dam tshig nyams chag thams cad skong gyur cig /
NK008(nya)001:2277: rnal 'byor bdag gi dpal dang sdong grogs mdzod //
NK008(nya)001:2278: ya mtshan bswe yi ra skyes kham pa ni //
NK008(nya)001:2279: brjid pa'i nyams ldan mdzes pa'i dar gyis brgyan //
NK008(nya)001:2280: rgya dang smin ma ag tshom rab tu dkar //
NK008(nya)001:2281: drang srong me yi lha dang bdud kyi rta //
NK008(nya)001:2282: brag btsan dmar po'i bzhon pa mi yi nor //
NK008(nya)001:2283: khyu longs rdzi bo bskos ba grangs med kyis //
NK008(nya)001:2284: sgrol ging dmar po 'khor bcas thugs dam bskang //
NK008(nya)001:2285: dam tshig nyams chag thams cad skong gyur cig /
NK008(nya)001:2286: rnal 'byor bdag gi dpal dang sdong grogs mdzod //
NK008(nya)001:2287: gcan gzan rgyal po seng ge rngam zhing mchong //
NK008(nya)001:2288: stag gzig don dang 'phar ba lce spyang dang //
NK008(nya)001:2289: wa dang spyang gi dregs pa'i nga ro sgrogs //
NK008(nya)001:2290: rab 'jigs sha sna dmar po dgra la za //
NK008(nya)001:2291: dmar chen khrag gi btung bas rab myos pa'i //
NK008(nya)001:2292: dur khrod nyul ba'i gcan gzan grangs med kyis //
NK008(nya)001:2293: sgrol ging dmar po 'khor bcas thugs dam bskang //
NK008(nya)001:2294: dam tshigs nyams chag thams cad skong gyur cig /
NK008(nya)001:2295: rnal 'byor bdag gi dpal dang sdong grogs mdzod //
NK008(nya)001:2296: mchog tu mi 'gyur gang la chags pa'i rten //
NK008(nya)001:2297: gling bzhi ri rab gling phran bcas pa la //
NK008(nya)001:2298: zhal nam dmar po zer mo'i phod kyis brgyan //
NK008(nya)001:2299: nam rgyang sna tshogs bkrag mdangs ya la la //
NK008(nya)001:2300: mthun pa'i bya skad sna tshogs nye re re //
NK008(nya)001:2301: skye 'gro'i sems can mang po shigs se shig /
NK008(nya)001:2302: gsang ba'i mdos chen sprin ltar gtibs pa 'dis //
NK008(nya)001:2303: sgrol ging dmar po 'khor bcas thugs dam bskang //
NK008(nya)001:2304: dam tshig nyams chag thams cad skong gyur cig /
NK008(nya)001:2305: rnal 'byor bdag gi dpal dang sdong grogs mdzod //
NK008(nya)001:2306: rten las ma 'da' 'ben las ma g.yos shig /
NK008(nya)001:2307: dngos bshams yid sprul mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK008(nya)001:2308: sangs rgyas bstan srungs dkon mchog dbu 'phang bstod //
NK008(nya)001:2309: gnas dang yul srungs 'khor dang gang zag skyongs //
NK008(nya)001:2310: 'bru dang mi rgyud rin chen gang zag spel //
NK008(nya)001:2311: lha 'dre mi gsum 'byung po dbang du sdus //
NK008(nya)001:2312: dkor la rku 'phrog byed rnams thams cad thul //
NK008(nya)001:2313: 'gro na lam gyi 'jigs pa srungs shing sgrol //
NK008(nya)001:2314: rbad 'dre mthu gtad khyed kyis phyir la bzlog /
NK008(nya)001:2315: snyan pa grags pa phyogs bcu kun tu sgrogs //
NK008(nya)001:2316: thugs dam ma g.yel phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK008(nya)001:2317: rnal 'byor bdag cag 'khor dang bcas rnams kyi //
NK008(nya)001:2318: mi mthun rkyen dang bar chad zhing ba dang //
NK008(nya)001:2319: tshe dang bsod nams dpal 'byor rgyas par mdzod //
NK008(nya)001:2320: log par lta ba ma lus dbang du sdus //
NK008(nya)001:2321: gnod byed dgra bgegs ma lus dbang du bsdus //
NK008(nya)001:2322: rdul phran bzhin du rlog bya ba'ang 'dug /
NK008(nya)001:2324: mchog dang thun mong dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK008(nya)001:2325: bstan pa dar zhing rgyas pa'i phrin las mdzod //
NK008(nya)001:2326: ces brjod phud gtor phrin las bcol /
NK008(nya)001:2328: ru mtshon dmar gso ba'i yang snang /
NK008(nya)001:2330: gshin rje dmar po'i las byang bzhugs so //
NK008(nya)001:2332: snang srid rak+ta'i gzhal yas nas //
NK008(nya)001:2333: gshin rje dmar po mi zan te //
NK008(nya)001:2334: sgrol gang bdag po ma ru rtse //
NK008(nya)001:2335: dam nyams srogs gi gshed du gshegs //
NK008(nya)001:2337: srin mo khrag mig ral ba can //
NK008(nya)001:2338: dpal ldan nag mo re ma ti //
NK008(nya)001:2339: dam nyams srog gi gshed du gshegs //
NK008(nya)001:2340: shar phyogs srin po'i yul rtse nas //
NK008(nya)001:2341: srin po gnod sbyin ma ru rtse //
NK008(nya)001:2342: srin po mi zan 'bum gyis bskor //
NK008(nya)001:2343: dam nyams srog gi gshed du gshegs //
NK008(nya)001:2344: lho phyogs gshin rje'i yul rtse nas //
NK008(nya)001:2345: gshin rje gnod sbyin ma ru rtse //
NK008(nya)001:2346: gshin rje mi zan 'bum gyis bskor //
NK008(nya)001:2347: dam nyams srog gi gshed du gshegs //
NK008(nya)001:2348: nub phyogs bdud kyi yul rtse nas //
NK008(nya)001:2349: bdud po gnod sbyin ma ru rtse //
NK008(nya)001:2350: bdud po mi zan 'bum gyis bskor //
NK008(nya)001:2351: dam nyams srog gi gshed du gshegs //
NK008(nya)001:2352: byang phyogs gnod sbyin yul rtse nas //
NK008(nya)001:2353: ku be r+aa dza gter gyi bdag /
NK008(nya)001:2354: gnod sbyin mi zan 'bum gyis bskor //
NK008(nya)001:2355: dam nyams srogs gi gshed du gshegs //
NK008(nya)001:2356: gzhan yang khrag skyug shan pa'i tshogs //
NK008(nya)001:2357: bal mo nag mo snying zan dang //
NK008(nya)001:2358: sgrol ging lce spyang rngams pa'i tshogs //
NK008(nya)001:2359: dam nyams srog gi gshed du gshegs //
NK008(nya)001:2360: e h+ye hi sh+r+ai man+dzu ya m+aan+ta ka e ka dz+aa ti ya ho phata /
NK008(nya)001:2367: dzahmh'u bam hoh a gad dza ya /
NK008(nya)001:2370: brtan par bzhugs par bsam la /
NK008(nya)001:2372: lcang lor bcas pa'i mtshan ldan ka p+aa la //
NK008(nya)001:2373: 'chi med bdud rtsi rak+ta dmar gyis bkang //
NK008(nya)001:2374: mar khu khrag zhag sbrang rtsi 'o mar bcas //
NK008(nya)001:2375: sgrol ging bdag po cho srog ma ru rtse //
NK008(nya)001:2376: srin po gshin rje bdud dang gnod sbyin dang //
NK008(nya)001:2377: nad kyi bdag po sa bdag snying zan bzhi //
NK008(nya)001:2378: sprul pa yang sprul sgrol ging 'bum gyis bskor //
NK008(nya)001:2379: rab tu khros pa'i lha tshogs khyed la 'bul //
NK008(nya)001:2380: bstan bshigs dgra bo myur du bsgral ba dang //
NK008(nya)001:2381: rnal 'byor bsam don 'grub pa'i phrin las mdzod //
NK008(nya)001:2382: +amo sh+r+ai many+dzu ya ma r+aa dza e ka tsa ti /
NK008(nya)001:2385: ma h+aa kem ni ri ti ma h+aa pany+tsa a
NK008(nya)001:2386: mri ta i dam ba ling+ta kha kha kh+aa hi
NK008(nya)001:2387: kh+aa hi / +amo ya ho phata kha kha kh+aa hi /
NK008(nya)001:2388: ma ho phata kha kha kh+aa hi /
NK008(nya)001:2389: shu ho phata kha kha kh+aa hi /
NK008(nya)001:2390: ma ru rtse phata kha kha kh+aa hi /
NK008(nya)001:2391: rngam rngam phata kha kha kh+aa hi /
NK008(nya)001:2392: nyi phata kha kha kh+aa hi /
NK008(nya)001:2393: h'u h'u phata kha kha kh+aa hi /
NK008(nya)001:2394: dam can bshan pa dmar po 'khor dang bcas pa rnams kyis sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa srungs sogs /
NK008(nya)001:2396: dgra bo 'di zhes bya ba myur du sgrol ba'i phrin las mdzod cig /
NK008(nya)001:2398: rang gshed por gsal ba'i mdun du //
NK008(nya)001:2399: bshan pa 'khor dang bcas pa rang dbang med par
NK008(nya)001:2400: bka' nyan pa'i tshul du 'bar yed yed 'dug par
NK008(nya)001:2401: bsam la / bsnyen pa'i sngags 'di bzlas so //
NK008(nya)001:2409: zhes gsod pa'i sngags rtags ma byung bar du drag tu bazla'o //
NK008(nya)001:2410: 'di rnams shin tu gsang bar bya'o //
NK008(nya)001:2415: // // bcom ldan 'jam dpal gshin rje dmar po'i mdos kyi cho ga bzhugs so //
NK008(nya)001:2416: bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal gshin rje'i gshed po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK008(nya)001:2417: sgrol ging bdag po ma ru rtse la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK008(nya)001:2418: 'jam dpal ma ru rtse sku khros nas bdag la
NK008(nya)001:2419: tshur la gnod cing nad nyen can byung ba dang
NK008(nya)001:2420: / rnal 'byor pa la nyams len cing mtshan ma ngan pa ston pa la mdos 'di bya ste /
NK008(nya)001:2421: nyams chag skong ba'i mdos 'di la drug ste /
NK008(nya)001:2422: dang po mdos bshams pa dang /
NK008(nya)001:2428: dang po mdos bshams pa ni /
NK008(nya)001:2429: zan bre thag ma gcig las gru gsum bang rim gsum pa gcig byas la /
NK008(nya)001:2431: steng du sor gnyis gnyis gting du bru /
NK008(nya)001:2432: der gri khrag blug la bdud rtsi gdab /
NK008(nya)001:2433: de steng mkhar dmar mtho gang bzhag /
NK008(nya)001:2434: snyug ma tshig bdun gcig la yang //
NK008(nya)001:2435: nam mkha' dmar po bdun brtsegs dgod //
NK008(nya)001:2436: dar dmar ras ma dmar po yi //
NK008(nya)001:2437: lcang lo yang ni gdags par bya //
NK008(nya)001:2440: dar zab kyis kyang brgyan la gzugs //
NK008(nya)001:2441: nam mkha' khong nag 'ja' ris yang //
NK008(nya)001:2442: yum gyis rdzas su dgod par bya //
NK008(nya)001:2443: mda' nag 'phang nag ser mo can //
NK008(nya)001:2444: bya nag lugs nag yum gyi rdzas //
NK008(nya)001:2445: bswe mo yi ni rdzas la yang //
NK008(nya)001:2446: rigs dang mthun pa'i mi rta bzhi //
NK008(nya)001:2447: lug nag spyi dkar mgo ser dang //
NK008(nya)001:2448: smug mo sngo skya chu kha bzhi //
NK008(nya)001:2449: tsa ra rog po lte dkar rgya bo dang //
NK008(nya)001:2450: seng ge 'brug dang chu srin bzhi //
NK008(nya)001:2451: wa sbyang 'phar ba khyi dang bzhi //
NK008(nya)001:2452: ri rab gling bzhi'i phyogs mtshams su //
NK008(nya)001:2453: rim pa bzhin du dgod bskor la dgod kyang snang /
NK008(nya)001:2455: rnga mong rtol drel bong bu bzhi //
NK008(nya)001:2456: bya rgod khrung khrung bzhad dang ngang pa bzhi //
NK008(nya)001:2457: gong ltar rim pas bskor la dgod //
NK008(nya)001:2458: made'u thung zur gsum bzhi byas la //
NK008(nya)001:2459: de la bswe mdung bzhi btsug la //
NK008(nya)001:2460: rigs mthun dar gyi ba dan btags //
NK008(nya)001:2461: bswe mda' mkhar thabs bzhi byas la //
NK008(nya)001:2462: rdo rje rin po che dang ni //
NK008(nya)001:2463: pad+ma rgya gram bzhi bris la //
NK008(nya)001:2464: rigs dang mthun pa'i dar gyis brgyan //
NK008(nya)001:2466: dkyil 'khor bris la ri'u gtsos kyi brgyan //
NK008(nya)001:2467: nam mkha' nag po khong dkar khong dmar khong sngon la //
NK008(nya)001:2468: tha ma 'ja' tshon ris su bris //
NK008(nya)001:2469: bya spus brgyan pa mtshams bzhir gzugs //
NK008(nya)001:2470: ba spu dmar po'i ras kyis gtibs //
NK008(nya)001:2471: dar dang le brgan gur gyis phub //
NK008(nya)001:2472: de yi mtha' mar bshos bdun dgod //
NK008(nya)001:2473: seng ge bdun dang dre'u g.yag dang glang //
NK008(nya)001:2474: ma he ra lug bya khyi mi dmar bdun //
NK008(nya)001:2475: seng ge glang dang rta nag dang //
NK008(nya)001:2476: bswe yi bya khra zhon pa bzhi //
NK008(nya)001:2477: bswe yi bya khra g.yu gshog can dang bzhi //
NK008(nya)001:2478: bswe yi sbyang ki bzhi dang ni //
NK008(nya)001:2479: mi ring gri thogs bco brgyad kyis //
NK008(nya)001:2480: de rnams gun gyi mtha' bskor ro //
NK008(nya)001:2481: phud ni ma nyams bya'o gang //
NK008(nya)001:2482: de la sman yang btab la bzhag /
NK008(nya)001:2483: zan gyi zla gam dmar po bdun dgod do //
NK008(nya)001:2484: dpal gtor spyan gzigs sna tshogs can //
NK008(nya)001:2485: gshin rje dmar po'i gtor ma la //
NK008(nya)001:2486: sha chen khrag chen brgyan pa gcig /
NK008(nya)001:2487: phud dang rak+ta ci mang dbul //
NK008(nya)001:2488: ra lug bya yis thugs dam skong //
NK008(nya)001:2489: bdag nyid chas gos dmar po bgos //
NK008(nya)001:2490: thod ni dmar po gcig bcings la //
NK008(nya)001:2491: bdag nyid ya m+aan+ta ka sku mdog le brgan dang //
NK008(nya)001:2492: dbu drug phyag ni bcu gnyis la /
NK008(nya)001:2494: yi dwags dmar po'i gdan du bting ba /
NK008(nya)001:2495: phyag mtshan bcu gnyis spyi dang mthun pa /
NK008(nya)001:2496: byi ru'i sdong po bsgreng ba 'dra ba gcig shin tu gsal par bsgom mo //
NK008(nya)001:2497: de'i ngang la snying po brgya rtsa re 'don no //
NK008(nya)001:2498: gnyis pa byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NK008(nya)001:2499: mdos sngags drug phyag rgya drug gis byin gyis brlabs la /
NK008(nya)001:2503: gsum pa khungs btsal ba ni 'di skad do //
NK008(nya)001:2505: dang po mdos byung gang nas byung /
NK008(nya)001:2507: dang po glud byung gang nas byung //
NK008(nya)001:2508: glud byung rgya gar yul nas byung //
NK008(nya)001:2509: mdos byung rgya gar yul nas byung //
NK008(nya)001:2515: slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje dang /
NK008(nya)001:2516: rgya gar mkhas pa lnga brgya yis //
NK008(nya)001:2518: rgyal po'i khab kyi grong khyer nas /
NK008(nya)001:2524: cha gcig ri rab rtse la bskyal //
NK008(nya)001:2525: cha gcig gtsang chab gzhung la bskyal //
NK008(nya)001:2526: cha gcig sa yi gter du spas //
NK008(nya)001:2527: der ni mi nad rgyun kyang chad //
NK008(nya)001:2534: dang po glu dbyung gang nas byung //
NK008(nya)001:2535: dang po mdos byung gang nas byung //
NK008(nya)001:2536: glud byung rgya nag yul nas byung //
NK008(nya)001:2537: mdos byung rgya nag yul nag byung //
NK008(nya)001:2544: slob dpon ba ta thig le dang //
NK008(nya)001:2545: sgom mkhan g.yu yi sgron ma gnyis //
NK008(nya)001:2551: cha gcig ri rab rtse la bskyal //
NK008(nya)001:2552: cha gcig gtsang chab gzhung la bskyal //
NK008(nya)001:2553: cha gcig sa yi gter du spas //
NK008(nya)001:2554: der ni mi nad rgyun kyang chad //
NK008(nya)001:2561: dang po glud byung gang nas byung //
NK008(nya)001:2562: dang po mdos byung gang nas byung //
NK008(nya)001:2563: glud byung bod kyi yul nas byung //
NK008(nya)001:2564: mdos byung bod kyi yul nas byung //
NK008(nya)001:2570: der slob dpon pad+ma 'byung gnas dang //
NK008(nya)001:2571: 'dre ni rgyal ba'i blo gros kyis //
NK008(nya)001:2578: cha gcig ri rab rtse nas bskyal //
NK008(nya)001:2579: cha gcig gtsang chab gzhung la bskyal //
NK008(nya)001:2580: cha gcig sa yi gter du spas //
NK008(nya)001:2581: der ni mi nad rgyun kyang chad //
NK008(nya)001:2587: de ring sngags 'chang rgyal po bdag /
NK008(nya)001:2596: bzhi pa spyan drang ba 'di lta ste /
NK008(nya)001:2598: dad pa dag ni dam tshig gis //
NK008(nya)001:2599: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs khro rgyal che //
NK008(nya)001:2600: khro rgyal gshin rje sgrol ging bdag /
NK008(nya)001:2601: 'phags pa'i rgyal po srog bdag gnod sbyin ma ru rtse //
NK008(nya)001:2602: gshin rje dmar po srog bdag dbugs kyi bdag /
NK008(nya)001:2603: nye ring med par 'joms pa'i gshin rje'i gshed //
NK008(nya)001:2604: thams cad brlag par mdzad pa'i gshin rje'i gshed //
NK008(nya)001:2605: srog bdag dmar po spyan 'dren no //
NK008(nya)001:2606: sgrol ging chen po spyan 'dren no //
NK008(nya)001:2607: las kyi gshin rje spyan 'dren no //
NK008(nya)001:2608: mdos la spyan 'dren gshegs su gsol //
NK008(nya)001:2610: yum chen e ka dz+aa ti spyan 'dren no //
NK008(nya)001:2611: ma tshogs stong gi bdag mo spyan 'dren no //
NK008(nya)001:2612: 'jig rten nad kyi bdag mo spyan 'dren no //
NK008(nya)001:2613: nag mo 'bum gyi bdag mo spyan 'dren no //
NK008(nya)001:2614: lce spyang nag mo spyan 'dren no //
NK008(nya)001:2615: mdos la spyan 'dren gshegs su gsol //
NK008(nya)001:2617: srog zan mched bzhi ging gi tshogs //
NK008(nya)001:2618: sgrol ging bdag po 'bum dang bcas //
NK008(nya)001:2619: dgra dang bgegs la las kha bsgyur //
NK008(nya)001:2620: dam nyams srog la rngam zas byed //
NK008(nya)001:2621: mdos la spyan 'dren gshegs su gsol //
NK008(nya)001:2623: dam can bswe yi lha mo'i tshogs //
NK008(nya)001:2624: gcig dang 'dra ba'i mched sde bzhi //
NK008(nya)001:2625: sring mo mched bzhi mthu mo che //
NK008(nya)001:2626: rgya gar yul gyi dbang bsgyur ma //
NK008(nya)001:2627: bal po yul gyi phung byed ma //
NK008(nya)001:2628: bal po mthil gyi bdud 'dul mo //
NK008(nya)001:2629: tsha ba rong gi gza' 'dul ma //
NK008(nya)001:2630: mang yul bse yi btsan 'dul ma //
NK008(nya)001:2632: bal yul yang le shod du ni //
NK008(nya)001:2633: rdzu 'phrul dag kyang che ba'i yum //
NK008(nya)001:2634: bswe yi lha mo mched sde bzhi //
NK008(nya)001:2635: slob dpon pad+ma thod phreng gis //
NK008(nya)001:2636: thugs dam mnyam sbyor dgyes 'khril zhing //
NK008(nya)001:2637: rgya gar yul gyi dbus 'gyur tshal //
NK008(nya)001:2639: sgrub gnas de ru dam bcas pa //
NK008(nya)001:2640: phur pa rdo rje gzhon nu'i grogs //
NK008(nya)001:2641: sgrub pa po yi mthu bskyed cing //
NK008(nya)001:2642: dam tshig can gyi grogs bya zhing //
NK008(nya)001:2643: khas blang de ni dam bcas bzhin //
NK008(nya)001:2644: sgrub pa po la grogs mdzod phyir //
NK008(nya)001:2645: mdos la spyan 'dren gshegs su gsol //
NK008(nya)001:2646: 'khor gyi shan pa mi bdun 'khor dang bcas pa spyan 'dren no //
NK008(nya)001:2647: gri thogs ging chen bcu bzhi 'khor dang bcas //
NK008(nya)001:2648: khram thogs bdud bcu 'khor dang bcas //
NK008(nya)001:2649: dmar nag bswe yi ging chen 'bum sde ste //
NK008(nya)001:2650: bskang rdzas mdos brgyad cu rtsa gcig gzugs dang mdangs la ni /
NK008(nya)001:2651: nyams chag bskang phyir lcam dral 'khor bcas gshegs su gsol /
NK008(nya)001:2652: +amo many+dzu sh+r+ai ku m+aa ra ma ru rtse be ta li s+w+aa h+aa /
NK008(nya)001:2653: dza h'u bam hoh dzahdzah be ta li dzah h'u
NK008(nya)001:2654: bam ho dzahdzah dmag dpon bzhi la dzahmh'u bam hohdzahdzah
NK008(nya)001:2655: bal mo bzhi la dzahmh'u bam hoh 'khor sprul ba
NK008(nya)001:2656: la dzah h'u bam hoh dzahdzah arka dza ya h'u
NK008(nya)001:2657: dzahdzah lnga pa bsngosa gdab pa ni /
NK008(nya)001:2660: ri rab gleng gzhi'i gzhal yas dang //
NK008(nya)001:2661: dmar nag gru gsum 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK008(nya)001:2662: bswe dmar 'bum gyi dmag dpon mdzad //
NK008(nya)001:2663: sgrol ging dmar po gshin rje'i gshed kyi lha //
NK008(nya)001:2664: ral pa kham nag gyen du 'khyil ba yis //
NK008(nya)001:2665: sum cu rtsa gsum lha rnams kun kyang 'dar zhing basngangasa /
NK008(nya)001:2666: spyan gsum sdang mig gyen du ldog pa yis //
NK008(nya)001:2667: phyogs bcu'i khro rgyal rnams kyang gan bug 'gyel //
NK008(nya)001:2668: smin ma glog stong 'od du 'bar ba yis //
NK008(nya)001:2669: sprul pa'i pho nya rnams kyis stong gsum 'geng //
NK008(nya)001:2670: mche ba zla tshes dkar po gtsigs pa yis //
NK008(nya)001:2671: dam nyamasadagra bgegs rba klong rtsad nas gcod //
NK008(nya)001:2672: zhal nas khro bo gad rgyangs bsgrags pa yis //
NK008(nya)001:2673: khams gsum srid pa gsum yang 'gul zhing ldeg /
NK008(nya)001:2674: phyag mtshan rdo rje me rlung 'khor lo bsnams pa yis //
NK008(nya)001:2675: sdang ba'i dgra bo thal bar rlog /
NK008(nya)001:2676: glang chen ko rlon ya ba gyon //
NK008(nya)001:2677: log par lta ba'i dgra bgegs rdul du rlog /
NK008(nya)001:2678: me ri dmar nag 'bar ba'i klong na bzhugs //
NK008(nya)001:2679: bcom ldan 'jam dpal sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK008(nya)001:2680: sgrol ging chen po mdos kyis thugs dam bskang //
NK008(nya)001:2681: brgyad cu rtsa bzhi gzugs dang mdangs kyis thugs dam bskang //
NK008(nya)001:2682: bshos chen dmar po bdun gyis thugs dam bskang //
NK008(nya)001:2683: rmad byung tsit+ta ma h+aa rak+ta byang chub sems //
NK008(nya)001:2684: ro mchog gser skyems bdud rtsi'i thugs dam bskang //
NK008(nya)001:2685: 'dir byon tshe srog klud bzhes la //
NK008(nya)001:2686: ngan pa bzlog la gdug pa choms //
NK008(nya)001:2688: g.yon nas yum bskyed e ka dz+aa ti ma /
NK008(nya)001:2689: srid pa'i ma mo mthu mo che //
NK008(nya)001:2690: sku ni nam mkha'i stong dang mnyam //
NK008(nya)001:2691: sku mdog smug nag tse re re //
NK008(nya)001:2692: mthing nag ral pa nyi li li //
NK008(nya)001:2693: spyan gsum sdang mig khro gnyer can //
NK008(nya)001:2694: zhal gdangs pa la mche ba gtsigs //
NK008(nya)001:2695: bzhugs ni sa sbra'i 'og na bzhugs //
NK008(nya)001:2696: lu chu khron pa'i drod 'bebs ma //
NK008(nya)001:2697: rgya mtsho'i gting na bzhugs tsam na //
NK008(nya)001:2698: 'bras bu lo tog bcud bsdud ma //
NK008(nya)001:2699: rlung nag 'tshubs ma'i nang na bzhugs tsam na //
NK008(nya)001:2700: rtsi shing nags tshal kha 'bus ma //
NK008(nya)001:2701: nam mkha'i dkyil na bzhugs tsam na //
NK008(nya)001:2702: thog dang ser ba shwa rgal 'bebs //
NK008(nya)001:2703: sku la smug nag brjid pa gsol //
NK008(nya)001:2704: rma bya'i mdangs kyi sham thabs can //
NK008(nya)001:2705: phyag g.yas tsit+ta t+r+ai shul rtse gsum bsnams //
NK008(nya)001:2706: dgra bo dug gsum rtsad nas gcod //
NK008(nya)001:2707: phyag g.yon lci spyad b+han+ha dmar bkang bsnams //
NK008(nya)001:2708: dam nyams dgra la khrag thun char ltar 'bebs //
NK008(nya)001:2709: chibs su dre'u smug po chibs /
NK008(nya)001:2710: chibs kyi snga long phyi long la mi ro rta ro phru lu lu //
NK008(nya)001:2711: nad rkyal tshon gru 'phong la bkal //
NK008(nya)001:2712: rnal 'byor spyi yi srung ma ru //
NK008(nya)001:2713: gzhan gyis ma bcol rang gi zhal 'ches pa //
NK008(nya)001:2714: bya lug ra khyi dmar po'i srog snying bdag /
NK008(nya)001:2715: bskang ngo ma yi rgyal mo mdos bzhes cig /
NK008(nya)001:2716: ma la mchod pa 'bul ba ni /
NK008(nya)001:2717: 'bru lnga bsres pa'i zhal zas dang //
NK008(nya)001:2718: dam rdzas bam gyi tsit+ta dang //
NK008(nya)001:2719: rgya bo khyi yi snying khrag dang //
NK008(nya)001:2720: sha khrag dmar gyi gtor ma dang //
NK008(nya)001:2721: bdud rtsi sman gyi mchod pa 'bul //
NK008(nya)001:2722: ma la 'bul lo bzhes su gsol //
NK008(nya)001:2723: 'dir byon tshe srog klud bzhes la //
NK008(nya)001:2724: mdos bdag chen pos mdos longs la //
NK008(nya)001:2725: klud bdag chen po klud bzhes shig /
NK008(nya)001:2726: ngan pa bzlog la gdug pa choms //
NK008(nya)001:2729: 'jam dpal spyan gyi rol pa las //
NK008(nya)001:2731: dmag dpon chen po gcig tu bsam //
NK008(nya)001:2732: shar gyi dmag dpon chen po ni //
NK008(nya)001:2733: bra ma r+aa dza srin po'i gtso //
NK008(nya)001:2734: khyod ni srin po ma ru rtse //
NK008(nya)001:2735: sku la 'gying dkar slog pa gsol //
NK008(nya)001:2736: rma chu sram gyi gong slag can //
NK008(nya)001:2737: dbu la dung gi rmog mo gsol //
NK008(nya)001:2738: dam nyams dgra la rngam tsam na //
NK008(nya)001:2739: yas kyi mche ba brang gi lhan snar sleb //
NK008(nya)001:2740: mas kyi mche bas smin mtshams sleb //
NK008(nya)001:2741: phyag na shel gyi zangs gri bsnams //
NK008(nya)001:2742: srog len srin po 'bum dang bcas //
NK008(nya)001:2743: srin po'i 'khor dang bcas pa la //
NK008(nya)001:2744: ma tram gzugs kyi thugs dam bskang //
NK008(nya)001:2745: gzugs glud brgyad cu rtsa gcig thugs dam bskang //
NK008(nya)001:2746: bshos chen dmar po bdun gyis thugs dam bskang //
NK008(nya)001:2747: rmad byung gtor mas thugs dam bskang //
NK008(nya)001:2748: ro mchog brgyad cu sbyar bas thugs dam bskar //
NK008(nya)001:2749: bskang ngo srin po 'khor bcas thugs dam bskang //
NK008(nya)001:2750: bshags so nyams chag so sor bshags //
NK008(nya)001:2751: bzlog cing rkyen ngan bar chad bzlog /
NK008(nya)001:2752: 'dir byon dam bskang phrin las mdzod //
NK008(nya)001:2753: ngan pa bzlog la gdug pa choms //

NK008(nya)001:2755: mdos bdag chen po mdos longs la //
NK008(nya)001:2756: glud bdag chen po glud bzhes shig /

NK008(nya)001:2764: khyod ni shin rje ma ru rtse //
NK008(nya)001:2765: ma he zhon nas phyogs bcur rgyug /
NK008(nya)001:2766: phyag na zhing gi dbyug tho bsnams //
NK008(nya)001:2767: srog len gshin rje 'bum dang bcas //
NK008(nya)001:2768: gshin rje 'khor dang bcas pa dang //

NK008(nya)001:2839: glu bdag chen pos glud bzhes shig /
NK008(nya)001:2840: dam tshig nyams pa sor chud cig /
NK008(nya)001:2842: bswe yi lha mo mched sde bzhi //
NK008(nya)001:2843: mdos la spyan 'dren gshegs su gsol //

NK008(nya)001:2845: bswe yi bud med chen mched sde snang mo bzhi //
NK008(nya)001:2846: nyi ma nub byang mtshams shed na //
NK008(nya)001:2847: bswe yi sku mkhar sgo bzhi na //
NK008(nya)001:2848: rin chen shel gyi ka ba can //
NK008(nya)001:2849: rin chen gser gyi kha bad can //
NK008(nya)001:2850: tha ma lcags ri 'bar bas bskor //
NK008(nya)001:2851: bswe mkhar 'bar ba'i rtse mo la //

NK008(nya)001:2864: a a ha ha'i sgra sgrogs shing //
