NK008(nya)001:5119: dam rdzas bdud rtsi lnga yi mchod pa 'bul //
NK008(nya)001:5120: bzhes nas mthu dang rtsal gyi dngos grub stsal du gsol /
NK008(nya)001:5121: dkar po gtsug gi rgyan gcig la //
NK008(nya)001:5122: dam rdzas bdud rtsi lnga yi mchod pa 'bul //
NK008(nya)001:5123: bzhes nas mthu dang rtsal gyi dngos grub stsal du gsol /
NK008(nya)001:5124: srin po'i ma mo 'bum khri 'bum stong la //
NK008(nya)001:5125: dam rdzas bdud rtsi lnga yi mchod pa 'bul //
NK008(nya)001:5126: bzhes nas mthu dang rtsal gyi dngos grub rtsal du gsol /
NK008(nya)001:5127: srog gshed chen po bzhi rnams la //
NK008(nya)001:5128: dam rdzas bdud rtsi lnga yi mchod pa 'bul //
NK008(nya)001:5129: bzhes nas mthu dang rtsal gyi dngos grub stsol //
NK008(nya)001:5130: zhes gtor ma la sman phud sbreng ngo //
NK008(nya)001:5132: sku mdog sngo nag gshin rje'i gshed kyi lha //
NK008(nya)001:5133: dug gsum mun khang 'joms pa'i mthu bo che //
NK008(nya)001:5134: rab 'jigs mtshungs med gshin rje'i gshed po la //
NK008(nya)001:5136: thugs dam bskul lo dgra la sa ma ya //
NK008(nya)001:5137: 'jigs byed chen po ya ma r+aa dza la //
NK008(nya)001:5139: thugs dam bskul lo dgra la sa ma ya //
NK008(nya)001:5140: shar phyogs srin po'i yul rtse nas //
NK008(nya)001:5141: srin po gnod sbyin ma ru rtse //
NK008(nya)001:5143: thugs dam bskul lo dgra la ma ya /
NK008(nya)001:5144: lho phyogs gshin rje'i yul rtse nas //
NK008(nya)001:5145: gshin rje gnod sbyin dmar po la //
NK008(nya)001:5147: thugs dam bskul lo dgra la sa ma ya //
NK008(nya)001:5148: nub phyogs bdud kyi yul rtse nas //
NK008(nya)001:5149: bdud po gnod sbyin dmar po la //
NK008(nya)001:5151: thugs dam bskul lo dgra la sa ma ya //
NK008(nya)001:5152: byang phyogs gnod sbyin yul rtse nas //
NK008(nya)001:5153: gnod sbyin gdug pa dmar po la //
NK008(nya)001:5155: thugs dam bskul lo dgra la sa ma ya //
NK008(nya)001:5156: dam can bswe yi lha mo mched bzhi la //
NK008(nya)001:5158: thugs dam bskul lo dgra la sa ma ya //
NK008(nya)001:5159: gshin rje'i 'khor na gnas pa'i dam can la //
NK008(nya)001:5161: thugs dam bskul lo dgra la sa ma ya //
NK008(nya)001:5164: thugs dam bskul lo dgra la sa ma ya //
NK008(nya)001:5165: bla med dam rdzas mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK008(nya)001:5166: sdang ba'i dgra la rtags phyung zhig /
NK008(nya)001:5167: rtags phyung rtsa ba drung nas phyungs //
NK008(nya)001:5168: dus mtha' bstungs la tshe yi 'du byed bskum //
NK008(nya)001:5169: lo zla zhag dang za mar ma bzhag par //
NK008(nya)001:5170: yid tsam cig la 'dir khug la //
NK008(nya)001:5171: da lta nyid du bsgral du gsol //
NK008(nya)001:5172: thugs dam bskul lo dgra la sa ma ya //
NK008(nya)001:5174: yang mngon pa'i rtags phyung zhig /
NK008(nya)001:5176: mi nub pa'i rgyal mtshan tshugs shig /
NK008(nya)001:5182: bya ba nan tan gyi gyer bskul rdzogs so //
NK008(nya)001:5185: nor sgrub pa gsum 'og tu las sna tshogs pa'i khongs su bsdu dgos gsungs so //
NK008(nya)001:5188: thod pa gling bzhi pa la spos chus legs par bkrus la /
NK008(nya)001:5189: gu gul gyi dud pas bdug /
NK008(nya)001:5190: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa bris la //
NK008(nya)001:5192: rtsibs mchan bzhi la ma bzhi dgod //
NK008(nya)001:5193: gur gum mam ldong ros kyis bris //
NK008(nya)001:5195: nang du sman sna tshogs dang /
NK008(nya)001:5200: de rnams la ril bu byas la blugs /
NK008(nya)001:5201: dar dmar pos dril la man+dala gyi thad kar bzhag /
NK008(nya)001:5203: +amo sh+r+ai ma ny+dzu ya ma r+aa dza /
NK008(nya)001:5204: ma ma e ka dz+aa ti dza dzah yak+sha ku
NK008(nya)001:5205: m+aa ra a yu dz+ny+aa na badz+ra a sha b+h+ru
NK008(nya)001:5207: de nas las sbyor dus su nyi shu rtsa re re bgrang ngo //
NK008(nya)001:5208: rgya gar d+ha na de las mdzad pa'o //
NK008(nya)001:5209: gcung yon tan rgya mtsho la gtad do //
NK008(nya)001:5212: 'jam dpal dmar po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK008(nya)001:5213: dmar po'i nor sgrub pa la /
NK008(nya)001:5214: mda' tshigs lnga pa la rgod sgro bskyon la //
NK008(nya)001:5215: de la dar dmar po'i khug mar 'bru sna lnga dang /
NK008(nya)001:5219: gzig ras dang byi ru rnams ra dmar po'i snying du blugs la /
NK008(nya)001:5220: sa bzang po bkra shis pa la rin po che brdar te /
NK008(nya)001:5221: de la bswe mkhar byas mda' gzugs so //
NK008(nya)001:5222: mda' la khug ma gdags so //
NK008(nya)001:5225: +amo sh+r+ai man+dzu ya ma r+aa dza ma ma e
NK008(nya)001:5226: ka dz+aa ti dza dzah +aar+ya dzam+b+ha la push+tim ku
NK008(nya)001:5228: yak+sha yak+sha sid+d+hi sid+d+hi s+w+aa h+aa /
NK008(nya)001:5229: zhes pa de dang po stong /
NK008(nya)001:5230: de nas las la sbyar ba'i dus su nyi shu rtsa re bzlas ba'o //
NK008(nya)001:5231: rgya gar d+ha na da las mdzad pa'o //
NK008(nya)001:5232: des yon tan rgya mtsho la gtad do //
NK008(nya)001:5233: +amo sh+r+ai many+dzu ya ma r+aa dzah e ka dz+aa
NK008(nya)001:5234: ti dza dzah +aar+ya dzam b+ha la dza len+t+ra ye
NK008(nya)001:5235: push+tim ku ru ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK008(nya)001:5236: yak+sha yak+sha rat+na sid+d+hi push+tim ku ru ye s+w+aa h+aa //
NK008(nya)001:5237: lha rje jo rdor gyi khyad chos so //
NK008(nya)001:5238: 'jam dpal dmar po'i sri'u gso ba'i man ngag 'di
NK008(nya)001:5239: la sri'u la 'jam dpal dmar po'i sku gsung thugs
NK008(nya)001:5241: bswe phor dmar po'i nang du /
NK008(nya)001:5242: dpal bshos zur gsum dmar po zhal dang bcas pa la /
NK008(nya)001:5243: zla gam dmar po bswe zhal can /
NK008(nya)001:5244: chang phud ma nyams pa rin po che /
NK008(nya)001:5245: yam shud dag la rtag tu btags /
NK008(nya)001:5247: +amo sa ma ya ra tri shang hri zhal du zhil zhil s+w+aa h+aa /
NK008(nya)001:5248: mda' bya rgod ma gcig la dar ser po gcig /
NK008(nya)001:5251: bswe'i bla gur tshe rta bsdoms /
NK008(nya)001:5253: +amo +aahmh'u h+r+aih many+dzu ya ma r+aa dzah ma ma e kha dz+aa ri dza dzahmh'u b+h+r+au s+w+aa h+aa /
NK008(nya)001:5257: ging gdong du ging bshos bcug nas kha byang du bltas te /
NK008(nya)001:5258: +amo sh+r+ai ta dzu ni kro d+ha ni /
NK008(nya)001:5261: shu la shu la d+ha sha g+h+ri ba d+ha sha g+h+ri ba h'u phata /
NK008(nya)001:5262: ba lim ta kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK008(nya)001:5265: 'jam dpal dmar po'i sri'u gso ba'o //
NK008(nya)001:5266: rgya gar d+ha na da las mdzad pa rdzogs so //
NK008(nya)001:5267: d+ha na da las gcung yon tan rgya mtsho la gnang ba'o //
NK008(nya)001:5268: lha rje seng ge rgyal gyis lha rje chos dbang la gtad pa'o //
NK008(nya)001:5271: 'di dang tshig ris phra mo re tsam mi 'dra
NK008(nya)001:5272: ba'i tshan pa gcig 'dug kyang phan tshun bsdebs nas
NK008(nya)001:5273: 'di'i nang du tshang bar byas yod pas nges par
NK008(nya)001:5274: mdzod / brgyad pa las sna tshogs pa'i skor la tshe sgrub /
NK008(nya)001:5275: cog brdung sngags kyi bzla lugs /
NK008(nya)001:5276: bsad sngags sngags kyi pra khrid /
NK008(nya)001:5277: dmar po'i rtags yig lugs gnyis zhes tshe sgrub ma
NK008(nya)001:5278: gtogs tshan pa nyung ngu re snang bas de dag
NK008(nya)001:5279: ni / bdud rtsi'i tshe dbang zhes pa ma ru rtse'i tshe sgrub bzhugs so //
NK008(nya)001:5287: ma ru rtse'i sgrub pa bya ba'i don bstan to //
NK008(nya)001:5288: de yang dang po gnas btsal te /
NK008(nya)001:5291: de nas dam rdzas bsag go //
NK008(nya)001:5292: ri bo chen por rab tu dben par 'di'i yon tan du grub pa ste gnas mi mthun /
NK008(nya)001:5301: de nas man+dala bri ba ni /
NK008(nya)001:5302: dbus lte ba zlum po la pad+ma 'dab brgyad du bri /
NK008(nya)001:5303: rdo rje'i ra ba dang gru chad sgo 'khyud ldan par bya'o //
NK008(nya)001:5306: gru chad ser po sgo rigs dang mthun /
NK008(nya)001:5307: dbus su ya m+aan+ta ka yab yum /
NK008(nya)001:5309: rdo rje slob dpon 'khor dang bcas pa /
NK008(nya)001:5310: sgo la phyag rgya mo bzhi dgod /
NK008(nya)001:5311: dbus su dngul bum gcig gi nang du /
NK008(nya)001:5313: sman dang 'o mar bsres la khrus bya /
NK008(nya)001:5314: pad+ma'i shar du dung gi bum pa /
NK008(nya)001:5316: nub tu zangs kyi bum pa /
NK008(nya)001:5317: byang du mthing shun bum pa /
NK008(nya)001:5318: dmod btsug la tshe g.yung ba 'phang /
NK008(nya)001:5319: de rnams shom na bsham mo //
NK008(nya)001:5320: de ltar ma shom na dbus kyi bum pa la bsdu'o //
NK008(nya)001:5321: zhag gcig tu phur bu byas la /
NK008(nya)001:5322: dang po tshe phur bsgrub ste bgegs kyi bar thag ma chod pas so //
NK008(nya)001:5327: tsakra bsdebs pa'i bag chags khrus bya /
NK008(nya)001:5328: de nas tshe sgrub kyi man+dala bri zhing /
NK008(nya)001:5330: pad+ma d+ha ra zhes thig gdab /
NK008(nya)001:5331: dbus thig bzhi gdab pa'i thig le dgu /
NK008(nya)001:5332: ling rtse bzhi la pad+ma 'dab brgyad re bri /
NK008(nya)001:5333: de'i phyi rim la rdo rje'i ra ba sgo 'khyud dang ldan pa bri /
NK008(nya)001:5340: gru chad ljang gu sgo rigs dang bstun /
NK008(nya)001:5342: dbus su ya m+aan+ta ka yab yum /
NK008(nya)001:5343: shar du ma ru rtse yab yum /
NK008(nya)001:5344: lhor ya ma r+aa dza yab yum /
NK008(nya)001:5345: nub tu myos byed 'bar ba yab yum /
NK008(nya)001:5346: byang du ral pa tshar dgu yab yum dgod /
NK008(nya)001:5347: grwa bzhir bswe mo mched bzhi dgod //
NK008(nya)001:5348: sgo la re ma t+ai bzhi dgod //
NK008(nya)001:5349: de nas rdzas dgod pa ni /
NK008(nya)001:5350: bkra shis mtshan ldan rdo rje ka /
NK008(nya)001:5351: yi ge h'u shong bu yod pas srid pa gsum dbang du bsdud pa mang po yod pa'o //
NK008(nya)001:5352: p+aa dum bu gcig pa shong bu bzhi pa /
NK008(nya)001:5353: la'am kun la dbang byed dpal ldan lcang lo can nam /
NK008(nya)001:5355: tshe 'phel rdo rje ka p+aa la'ang //
NK008(nya)001:5356: yang na grub pa'i b+han+d+ha btsal lo //
NK008(nya)001:5357: dbus su bswe phor dmar po /
NK008(nya)001:5358: b+han+d+ha dmar po srub med pa /
NK008(nya)001:5359: srub med pa gcig gi nang du snying po lnga /
NK008(nya)001:5361: a yon tan zhag bdun na 'chi ba zlog ste med du mi rung ngo //
NK008(nya)001:5362: ru ra rnam par rgyal ba /
NK008(nya)001:5374: se ba 'di rnams tshang bar 'tshal lo //
NK008(nya)001:5388: de rnams gcig tu bsres la kha tshe zan gyis bcad /
NK008(nya)001:5389: de'i steng du ka p+aa la gcig gis kha bcad
NK008(nya)001:5390: la dar dmar pos dkris la gzungs thag btags la
NK008(nya)001:5391: bsgrub pa bya'o // phyogs kyi ling rtse la yang b+han+d+ha rang po re bzhag la /
NK008(nya)001:5392: so so'i snying po bri bar bya'o //
NK008(nya)001:5393: grwa bzhir mda' bzhi la dar sna bzhi btags la bzhag go //
NK008(nya)001:5394: phyi nas dar sna lngas gur phub /
NK008(nya)001:5395: dur khrod kyi rdzas kyis steng nas g.yog go //
NK008(nya)001:5396: de nas mtshams gcod bya ba ni /
NK008(nya)001:5397: bdag nyid khro bo zhal gsum phyag drug tu bsgom la /
NK008(nya)001:5398: thugs ka nas ta ki r+aa dza bsgoms te /
NK008(nya)001:5399: badz+ra ma ru rtse ta ki r+aa dza h'u zhes pas /
NK008(nya)001:5400: khro bo sku mdog dmar po gcig phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad du 'phros pas /
NK008(nya)001:5401: srid pa rlung gis mi thar bar bsgom /
NK008(nya)001:5403: sems dpa' khro rgyal khrag 'thung gtso //
NK008(nya)001:5404: thugs kyi sprul pa sgrol ging gshed //
NK008(nya)001:5405: tshe la gnod pa rdul du rlog /
NK008(nya)001:5406: bar der phyag mtshan drug gi mtshams bya'o //
NK008(nya)001:5407: phyogs skyong bcu po bskrad de /
NK008(nya)001:5408: de nas mtshams bya ba ni /
NK008(nya)001:5409: ye shes sems dpa'i thugs kyi man+dala nas /
NK008(nya)001:5410: rdo rje me dpung sprin dpung 'khrigs //
NK008(nya)001:5411: nye ba'i zhi ba'i cha lugs dang ldan pa /
NK008(nya)001:5412: snying po'i dus su sku mdog gser btso ma 'dra ba phyag na gser gyi bum pa bsnams pa'o //
NK008(nya)001:5414: +amo ru ru spu ru dz+wa la tish+tha sid+d+hi lo tsha ni sa rba tshe dang /
NK008(nya)001:5415: ar+tha sa d+ha ni +aa yu dz+ny+aa na b+han du /
NK008(nya)001:5416: ye shes lhas byin dbab pa /
NK008(nya)001:5417: a pa ra mi ta tshe b+h+r+au /
NK008(nya)001:5419: de skad bgrangs pa'i dus na spro bsdu bya'o //
NK008(nya)001:5420: ye shes kyi lha de rnams kyis gang ba srung
NK008(nya)001:5421: bar bya ba la bsrung nas bag chags med par
NK008(nya)001:5422: bya'o // chos ma gtogs pa de gnyis gti mug sor sor la yod par bya'o //
NK008(nya)001:5423: lha chen po des sems can thams cad snyam pa thon gcig pa'o //
NK008(nya)001:5425: mgona po zhes bya ba ni gshin rje'i dus su bya'o //
NK008(nya)001:5426: ye shes zhes bya ba ni thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes dang /
NK008(nya)001:5427: tshe zhes pa ni kun gyi tshe srog go //
NK008(nya)001:5428: dapaga meda ni 'khor dpag tu med pas bskor ba'o //
NK008(nya)001:5429: 'di lta bu'i don ma rig na gshin rjes tshe rku'o //
NK008(nya)001:5430: sgrub pa'i dus su sku mdog dkar po zhi ba'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa /
NK008(nya)001:5431: snying ya m+aan+ta ka ni bud+d+ha he ru ka'o //
NK008(nya)001:5433: +amo h+r+aihti ni na phyi'i dus na rnam snang yab yum gyi don gyi mtshams /
NK008(nya)001:5434: h'u h'u shan ti a ba na ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK008(nya)001:5435: de ltar dgongs rgyud gong bzhin bya'o //
NK008(nya)001:5437: mar spros pas rtog sgrib bag chags bsregs /
NK008(nya)001:5438: m+aan+ta ka'i rang bzhin bum pa lo tsha na ru bsgom /
NK008(nya)001:5439: tshe skyems sam tshe 'bras su snang ba ma ru rtse /
NK008(nya)001:5440: gzungs thag byang chub sems kyi lam //
NK008(nya)001:5441: bsnyen pa'i dus su 'od phar spro //
NK008(nya)001:5442: tshur 'dus pa las rnal 'byor pa'i bag chags dang /
NK008(nya)001:5443: sngon po'am dkar po gang yang rung la /
NK008(nya)001:5444: sems kyi mtshan nyid 'od dmar smug sna tshogs la 'dus khyab par 'phros shing 'phel nas /
NK008(nya)001:5445: bkrag dang gzim dngas je che je cher 'phel bar bsgom /
NK008(nya)001:5446: 'od ni dmar po las ye shes sems dpa' dang khrag gi me long tsam du bsdu'o //
NK008(nya)001:5447: nye ba'i bsnyen pa'i dus tshur bsdu /
NK008(nya)001:5448: sgrub pa'i dus su thugs ka'i ye shes sems dpa' la bsdu /
NK008(nya)001:5449: de nas 'khor gyi snying po la //
NK008(nya)001:5451: dz+ny+aa na shin+tam ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK008(nya)001:5452: +amo te dz+aa ya ma r+aa dza'i don du rtan te ru ka /
NK008(nya)001:5457: da la ral pa tshar dgu /
NK008(nya)001:5458: shan po sh+ain+tam ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK008(nya)001:5461: mud kar mu tri gri na /
NK008(nya)001:5466: +amo badz+ra ka rma he ra ru ka /
NK008(nya)001:5468: bcom ldan ya m+aan+ta ka ste /
NK008(nya)001:5469: thugs ka zla tshe sring ba dang bskyed pa /
NK008(nya)001:5471: byang chub sems kyi +aa yu dmar po 'di //
NK008(nya)001:5472: tshe gcig sgrub pa po yi tshe yin no //
NK008(nya)001:5474: bcom ldan sangs rgyas sku yi gtso //
NK008(nya)001:5475: sku mdog zhi ba chos kyi sku la bstod pa bstan /
NK008(nya)001:5476: dkar pa gangs ri 'tsher ba la //
NK008(nya)001:5477: rin chen rgyan dang do shal se mo do //
NK008(nya)001:5478: bcom ldan sku la rab tu brgyan //
NK008(nya)001:5479: tshe stsol srog skyobs bcom ldan tshogs //
NK008(nya)001:5480: tshe yi yum chen lo tsa ni //
NK008(nya)001:5481: yum la yang zhi ba chos kyi sku'o //
NK008(nya)001:5482: g.yas pa thabs kyi yab la 'khril //
NK008(nya)001:5483: g.yon pa rin chen za ma tog /
NK008(nya)001:5484: phyag rgya sna tshogs cir yang bsgyur //
NK008(nya)001:5485: 'gro ba yongs kyi tshe la dbang bsgyur ma //
NK008(nya)001:5486: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu nas //
NK008(nya)001:5487: sgrub pa po yi tshe khug gcig /
NK008(nya)001:5488: de nas tshe gshed bzhi dgug /
NK008(nya)001:5490: shar gyi phyogs nas 'dir dmar po yin pas gshed bzhi'i sna la 'byung /
NK008(nya)001:5492: ye shes lha chen ma ma ru badz+ra he ru kahru rtse //
NK008(nya)001:5493: dri za'i gnas nas tshe khug cig /
NK008(nya)001:5494: don du rdo rje sems dapa'o //
NK008(nya)001:5495: lho yi phyogs nas tshe 'gugs pa //
NK008(nya)001:5496: nag po ya ma r+aa dza ste //
NK008(nya)001:5497: gshin rje'i phyogs nas tshe khug cig /
NK008(nya)001:5498: don du rat+na he ru lags //
NK008(nya)001:5499: nub kyi phyogs nas tshe 'gugs pa //
NK008(nya)001:5500: myos byed 'bar ba khro rgyal gtso //
NK008(nya)001:5501: klu yi gnas nas tshe khug gcig /
NK008(nya)001:5502: don du pad+ma he ru lags //
NK008(nya)001:5503: byang gi phyogs nas tshe 'gugs pa //
NK008(nya)001:5504: ral pa tshar dgu 'bar ba ste //
NK008(nya)001:5505: gnod sbyin phyogs nas tshe khug cig /
NK008(nya)001:5506: don du karma he ru lags //
NK008(nya)001:5507: tshe tshe la gnod pa bsal ba'i /
NK008(nya)001:5508: la gnod pa'i bgegs mda' dar dkar pos g.yab cing 'brang rgyas la 'bod /
NK008(nya)001:5512: rdo rje yang phur srung ma mdzad pa'i tshe //
NK008(nya)001:5513: nags kyi lha mo rma bya'i mgrin //
NK008(nya)001:5514: mgon po gshin rje'i srung ma mdzad pa'i tshe //
NK008(nya)001:5515: dkar mo mgyogs byed lcags kyu ma //
NK008(nya)001:5516: rdo rje lcags kyus tshe longs la //
NK008(nya)001:5518: tshe dbang thams cad 'dir khug cig /
NK008(nya)001:5519: +aa yu dz+nya na b+h+ru ni dza dzah h'u rdo rje yang phur mthu mo che //
NK008(nya)001:5520: bdud rtsi sman gyi srung ma mdzad pa'i tshe //
NK008(nya)001:5521: rtsi yi lha mo grub mo /
NK008(nya)001:5522: tshe yi srung ma mdzad pa'i tshe //
NK008(nya)001:5524: bswe'i lha mo bzhis tshe dgug pa'o //
NK008(nya)001:5529: dkar mo zhi ba'i thod phreng can //
NK008(nya)001:5533: sngon mo g.yu yi lan phran can //
NK008(nya)001:5534: srid gsum gnas nas tshe khug cig /
NK008(nya)001:5537: dmar po mtshal gyi thig phran can //
NK008(nya)001:5538: rgyud drug gnas nas tshe khug cig /
NK008(nya)001:5541: ljang gu lcags kyi go dor can //
NK008(nya)001:5542: mchog gsum gnas nas tshe khug cig /
NK008(nya)001:5543: srid pa'i le brgan dar gyi g.yab 'dor ma //
NK008(nya)001:5544: srid pa'i ma cig g.yu na rol //
NK008(nya)001:5546: sgo la tshe'i re ma t+wis tshe 'gug pa /
NK008(nya)001:5547: don blon mo nag mo yin /
NK008(nya)001:5549: bswe yi ral pa sha ra ra //
NK008(nya)001:5550: g.yas na mda' bzang bya rgod bsnams //
NK008(nya)001:5551: g.yon na g.yu yi ga'u bsnams //
NK008(nya)001:5553: tshe bzhag gnas ni 'di yin no //
NK008(nya)001:5554: de nas tshe 'gugs pa'i snying po //
NK008(nya)001:5555: +amo sa ya m+aan+ta ka yab yum gyis dgug pa /
NK008(nya)001:5556: ma ya +aar+ya many+dzu sh+r+ai mu tra ya ma m+aan+ta
NK008(nya)001:5557: ka pany+tsa te ro ni h'u dzah +aa yu dz+ny+aa
NK008(nya)001:5558: na b+h+r+au n+ri dza a kar+sha ya a pa na
NK008(nya)001:5559: ya s+w+aa h+aa / tri ling ma ru rtses dgug pa /
NK008(nya)001:5560: shang ka +aa yu dz+ny+aa na b+h+r+auhn+ri dzah tsi pi bswe mos dgug pa /
NK008(nya)001:5561: ri dzi skra na sa ma ya /
NK008(nya)001:5562: a n+ri tri +aa yu dz+ny+aa na b+h+r+au dzah tsa pa ma ma tis dgug pa /
NK008(nya)001:5564: +aa yu she b+h+r+au dzah de nas dngos grub blang /
NK008(nya)001:5565: de nas dbang zhi bar bya ba /
NK008(nya)001:5567: pa ra tsa ta hri ti a pa na ya h'u h'u phata phata /
NK008(nya)001:5569: snod dbang du bsdus la las la gzud pa /
NK008(nya)001:5570: ti shan ti ma a pa na ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK008(nya)001:5571: hri ti a ne ti a ne a pa na ya s+aa h+aa /
NK008(nya)001:5572: +aa yu dz+ny+aa na g.yu sgrub pa'i tshe bsring ba /
NK008(nya)001:5573: rtse a pa na b+h+ru a b+hi shiny+tsa a a
NK008(nya)001:5574: ah ma ka la mi 'du a pa na ya
NK008(nya)001:5576: dus ma yin par 'chi ba bzlog pa dang /
NK008(nya)001:5579: g.yu rtse a pa na ya b+h+r+au s+w+aa h+aa /
NK008(nya)001:5580: hri ti sa ma nan a dus gsum du gsungs pa'i sngags /
NK008(nya)001:5582: de nas u tsa ma mthong ba la mthong bar bya ste /
NK008(nya)001:5584: dngul gyi bum pa'i nang du rtsi sman sna tshogs blug la /
NK008(nya)001:5585: kha rgyan dpag bsam shing la bya /
NK008(nya)001:5587: zhag gsum du snying po 'bum khri drug stong bgrang /
NK008(nya)001:5590: pa ra tsha tra a pa na ya s+aa h+aa /
NK008(nya)001:5592: 'khor lo'i phyag rgya bcas la shar ma bdun bdud gsum gyis srid brkus pa 'phrog pa'o //
NK008(nya)001:5593: dbang bskur ba'i dus su phyag bya /
NK008(nya)001:5595: de nas dbang don du mi gnyer ba la /
NK008(nya)001:5598: pu tra tsa na pa na a pa na ya
NK008(nya)001:5599: +aa yu dz+ny+aa na g.yu rtse la b+hi shin tsa
NK008(nya)001:5600: a pa / bum pa la bzlas pa'i sngags de stong khri bzlas so //
NK008(nya)001:5601: na ya b+h+r+au dzah pu na tsa na a pa na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK008(nya)001:5604: yon tan gyi le'u ma ru rtse'i tshe sgrub rdzogs so //
NK008(nya)001:5606: man ngag gis tshe sgrub pa'i phyir mi ldog pa'i cho ga /
NK008(nya)001:5607: dang po sgrub pa'i thod pa /
NK008(nya)001:5608: tshe'i bum pa bkra shis pa'i thod pa legs par bshams la /
NK008(nya)001:5609: nang du 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi la //
NK008(nya)001:5619: pra ma ya byang du gnod sbyin s+ya h+ya /
NK008(nya)001:5620: mtha' ma a kro bcu bdun /
NK008(nya)001:5622: nang du tshe'i rdzas mar tsh+wa /
NK008(nya)001:5626: bzang drug gla rtsi snying tshol dang //
NK008(nya)001:5627: tshe yi snying po dag kyang btsal //
NK008(nya)001:5628: sngon du 'gro ba'i cho ga dang //
NK008(nya)001:5629: phyi bshags dag kyang dag par bya //
NK008(nya)001:5630: thod pa dar dkar nang du bstums //
NK008(nya)001:5631: grub na dkyil 'khor dbus su bzhag /
NK008(nya)001:5632: 'gro na byes su khyer bar bya //
NK008(nya)001:5633: sdod na rang gi thad kar gdags //
NK008(nya)001:5634: dang po yi ge bcu bdun bzlas //
NK008(nya)001:5635: +amo a kro te ka ya m+aan+ta ka ha na ma tha b+hany+dza h'u phata /
NK008(nya)001:5636: tshe chen bzung ba'i mchog tu'o //
NK008(nya)001:5638: +amo +aahmh'u sh+r+ai many+dzu ya m+aan+ta ka ya ma r+aa
NK008(nya)001:5639: dza ma ma e ka dz+aa ti dza dzah tshe
NK008(nya)001:5640: yi snying po brgya tshar re //
NK008(nya)001:5641: +amo sh+r+ai many+dzu rtag par brgya tshar re /
NK008(nya)001:5642: gu h+ya sa ma ya +aa yu she h+au +aah las la sbyor dang thun dus tshe //
NK008(nya)001:5643: snying po bzlas shing tshe bzung ngo //
NK008(nya)001:5644: thod pa de la gzungs thag gdags //
NK008(nya)001:5646: many+dzu gu h+ya sa ma ya +aa yu she +amo b+h+r+au /
NK008(nya)001:5652: dpal rigs lnga rang gi lus la dgod /
NK008(nya)001:5653: lte bar rnam par snang mdzad do //
NK008(nya)001:5654: snying khar rdo rje sems dpa' 'o //
NK008(nya)001:5655: lce la snang ba mtha' yas so //
NK008(nya)001:5656: sna la rin chen 'byung ldan no //
NK008(nya)001:5657: barla la don yod grub pa'o //
NK008(nya)001:5658: sngon du sgrol ging dmar po bsam //
NK008(nya)001:5659: tshe'i sgrub pa rnams rnal 'byor pas bzung ba'i man ngag /
NK008(nya)001:5660: phrin las ni gzhung ma mo ltar bagyi'o //
NK008(nya)001:5662: slob dpon d+ha na da las mdzad pa /
NK008(nya)001:5663: dang po mthu sh+r+ai many+dzu byed zil gyis mnan pa dang gcig /
NK008(nya)001:5665: bsham sbrag drag sngags dang bdun /
NK008(nya)001:5667: ma grub pa 'khor ba ru bzlog pa dang bzhi'o //
NK008(nya)001:5669: tri ling shad du ch+gee mo bri /
NK008(nya)001:5670: thod pa'i ma thod la bri /
NK008(nya)001:5671: dri za'i ya k+sha rbad ch+gee mo bri /
NK008(nya)001:5672: phye ma kha rdor ch+gee mo bri /
NK008(nya)001:5673: ru ru pra pra ch+gee mo bri /
NK008(nya)001:5674: dum dum shig shig m+aa ra ya phata /
NK008(nya)001:5680: sha ra ma na s+yee ch+gee mo bri /
NK008(nya)001:5681: ma h+aa r+aa dza s+yee ch+gee mo bri /
NK008(nya)001:5682: na mo na na ta ku pa ra ch+gee mo bri /
NK008(nya)001:5686: gshin rje dmar po'i las tshogs bzhugs so //
NK008(nya)001:5687: thath+watah&a&a&ao rgyan gu ru pad+ma 'byung gnas kyi dmar po
NK008(nya)001:5688: srog gi reg chod gsang ba 'di'i cog brdung sngags
NK008(nya)001:5689: kyi bzla lugs gud du bkol shan pa'i drag sngags
NK008(nya)001:5690: dmod pa'i dam pa yin +amo sngon 'gro bsnyen pa
NK008(nya)001:5691: yin / sh+r+ai many+dzu ya ma r+aa dza e ka
NK008(nya)001:5692: dz+aa ti dza dzah sngon du bya ba'i bsnyen pa
NK008(nya)001:5693: ste bcu bzhi yi ge'i phreng ba yin 'bum phrag
NK008(nya)001:5694: gcig tu bzlas pa bya +amo las kyi bsnyen pa
NK008(nya)001:5695: yin / / ya ho phata ma ho phata ma
NK008(nya)001:5696: ho phata shu ho phata ma ru rtse phata rngam
NK008(nya)001:5697: rngam phata nyi phata h'u h'u phata shan pa dngos
NK008(nya)001:5698: su 'bod pa ste rtags ma byung bar du bzlas
NK008(nya)001:5699: dang nyi phata h'u h'u phata kyi bar nyi shu
NK008(nya)001:5700: rtsa gnyis shan pa 'bod pa'i sngags rgyun du 'di
NK008(nya)001:5701: la nan tan bya +amo ya ho phata ma ho
NK008(nya)001:5702: phata shu ho phata ma ru rtse phata rngam rngam
NK008(nya)001:5703: phata nyi phata h'u h'u phata rngam rngam dgra bo'i
NK008(nya)001:5704: srog la rngam dgra bo'i khrag la rngam dgra bo'i
NK008(nya)001:5705: rus la rngam dgra bo'i sha la rngam nyi phata
NK008(nya)001:5706: h'u h'u phata bzhi bcu zhe dgu sngags kyi phreng
NK008(nya)001:5707: ba yin sgrub cing rbad pa'i sngags su rigs +amo
NK008(nya)001:5708: ya ho phata ma ho phata shu ho phata ma
NK008(nya)001:5709: ru rtse phata rngam rngam phata nyi phata h'u h'u
NK008(nya)001:5710: phata rngam rngam dgra bo'i srog la rngam rngam rngam
NK008(nya)001:5711: dgra bo'i khrag la rngam rngam rngam dgra bo'i rus
NK008(nya)001:5712: la rngam rngam rngam dgra bo'i sha la rngam bsad
NK008(nya)001:5713: pa'i yi ge lnga bcu pa gnod sbyin bdud dang
NK008(nya)001:5714: gshin rje srin po sha rus srog rtsa khrag la
NK008(nya)001:5715: rbad lnga bcu nga gcig sa ma ya /
NK008(nya)001:5716: btags pa ni bsad pa'i sngags su shes par bya +amo phyi thun /
NK008(nya)001:5717: ya ma h'u tri rbad sa ma ya /
NK008(nya)001:5718: h+aum shu tri rbad ma ru tri ya ma phata
NK008(nya)001:5719: rmugs ma ru ch+gee mo rbad rbad nyi shu rtsa
NK008(nya)001:5721: phyi thun ra thod bsad pa'i sngags nang gi thun /
NK008(nya)001:5722: ya ma shu tri ch+gee mo rbad rbad ma ru
NK008(nya)001:5723: rmugs n+ri rmugs n+ri rbad rbad bco brgyad nang gi
NK008(nya)001:5724: thun sngags te spyang thod nang du bsad pa'i sngags
NK008(nya)001:5725: gsang thun / ya ma shu tri ya dun ma
NK008(nya)001:5726: ru rtse ngam pa ya rbad rmugs pa n+ri mugs
NK008(nya)001:5727: rbad rbad du rbad pa ya n+ri ch+gee mo rbad
NK008(nya)001:5728: rbad rbab gri thod par gsang nas te /
NK008(nya)001:5729: yi ge sum cu gsang thun sngags bzlog dkrugs rnal ma'i khong nas 'byung ma gnad gcod /
NK008(nya)001:5730: ru rtse tsa khrag tsit+ta phyung dgra bo'i srog la
NK008(nya)001:5731: thum ri la n+ri thums thums tsit+ta rbad rbad ya
NK008(nya)001:5732: srog rmugs tsit+ta rbud rbud rbad sha rbad gyogs tsit+ta
NK008(nya)001:5733: ku la rbad rbad yam rbad gsang rbad ram rbad
NK008(nya)001:5734: myogs rbad kham rbad rmugs rbad khams rbad myags ma
NK008(nya)001:5735: ru rtse dgra bo'i srog la rbad ya drug cu
NK008(nya)001:5736: re gnyis ming dang bcas drag po'i gnad gcod rag
NK008(nya)001:5737: sngags te srog rtsa gcod pa'i spu grir shes sa
NK008(nya)001:5739: ya ni bsad pa'i drag sngags yin rnal ma la
NK008(nya)001:5740: sogs skabs kyi drag sngags yin ma ru rtse shan
NK008(nya)001:5741: pa'i sngags kyi yang gces rdzogs so gatatargra o rgyan
NK008(nya)001:5742: pad+ma bdag 'dra yis bdun gsum las kyi thus ka
NK008(nya)001:5743: ruh bsad pa'i drag sngags 'di bzlas pas srog rtsa
NK008(nya)001:5744: gcod pa'i spu gri yin +amo sa ma ya phug
NK008(nya)001:5745: phug rtol rtol tsit+ta phyung snying kha ram tshal pa
NK008(nya)001:5746: tshal pa b+h+yo kham kham snying la kham phyung phyung
NK008(nya)001:5747: tsit+ta phyung tsag shu bam ril thum thugs snying la
NK008(nya)001:5748: ya snying khrag khong nas drongs la shog ch+gee mo
NK008(nya)001:5749: m+aa ra ya rbad bla rtags byung nas bsad sngags
NK008(nya)001:5750: 'di zhag gsum bar du bzlas pa bya snying phyung
NK008(nya)001:5751: stobs pa dngos su 'byung bstan pa mnan te phur
NK008(nya)001:5752: pas gdab bshas zin sha khrag khyer ba dang tsit+ta
NK008(nya)001:5753: khyer nas byung na las byas pas shan pa'i tshogs
NK008(nya)001:5754: la gtang rag btang bar bya a na tha i
NK008(nya)001:5755: ti th+ra ka na o rgyan slob dpon pad+ma bdag
NK008(nya)001:5756: 'dra yis shan pa srog la rgol ba'i ma ru
NK008(nya)001:5757: rtse phyi nang gsang ba'i sngags kyi don bsdebs pa'i
NK008(nya)001:5758: drag po cog brdung sngags kyi pra khrid bri phyi
NK008(nya)001:5759: gcig tu / nang gsang ba gsang chen dril ba
NK008(nya)001:5760: las phyi sgrub dus su ra thod nang du ling+ga
NK008(nya)001:5761: gzhug spyang thod dpral bar shan pa'i drag sngags bri
NK008(nya)001:5762: nyin gyi dus su sgrub sngags /
NK008(nya)001:5763: srog la khrag la khrag rus la /
NK008(nya)001:5764: la rngam rngam tshan bzhi po btags la brab mtshan
NK008(nya)001:5765: gyi dus su sgrub pa'i sngags la thun sngags phyi
NK008(nya)001:5766: thun / dag kyang btags la brab skabs su thod pa 'thab ra sbyang gnyis /
NK008(nya)001:5767: tu gzhug zer gsum nyi zer zla zer skar zer /
NK008(nya)001:5768: dus su bla tshe dgug bla rtags nyams su lon
NK008(nya)001:5769: pa dang zhag gsum bsad pa'i sngags brab la ra
NK008(nya)001:5770: thod ling+ga gzhug par gtad klu la /
NK008(nya)001:5771: nang sgrub dus su spyang thod /
NK008(nya)001:5773: ling+ga brub nyin mtshan sngags ni de bzhin bsdebs gsang
NK008(nya)001:5774: sgrub dus su rnal gri'i thod par bsad thun sngags
NK008(nya)001:5775: phyi nang thun bsad pa dang sbrel /
NK008(nya)001:5776: gsang bar dbye gzhan nyin mtshan /
NK008(nya)001:5777: ma gong dang mthun par bya'o gsang chen gcig tu
NK008(nya)001:5778: dril ba la ra spyang gnyis kyi thod pa gnyis
NK008(nya)001:5779: btsal la ra thod nang du ling+ga gzhug brub khung
NK008(nya)001:5780: nang du ra thod kyi ling+ga gzhug par bya'o spyang
NK008(nya)001:5781: thod dmar po'i gsang sngags bris 'khor lo ro ras
NK008(nya)001:5782: dag la bri 'khor los spyang thod rab bstums la
NK008(nya)001:5783: tshon skur rgya gram bcing bar bya spyang thod nang
NK008(nya)001:5785: ling ga gzhug ra thod kyi /
NK008(nya)001:5791: chad du dug dang khrag dang yungs kar gsum bsnyen pa'i dus na bsgrub /
NK008(nya)001:5793: par bya spyang gi'i thod par gzhug par bya'o de
NK008(nya)001:5794: la gsang sngags bstim zhing bzlas bsad pa'i dus su
NK008(nya)001:5800: sngags dang thun sngags sa ma shu tri la /
NK008(nya)001:5801: sbrel skabs su rngam chen bzhi yi sngags kyis brab
NK008(nya)001:5802: zhag grangs bdun gyi bar dag tu sngags kyi grong
NK008(nya)001:5803: khyer sbrel bar bya ra thod ling+ga la bsad pa
NK008(nya)001:5804: / thun gyis brab las rdzogs ra thod pas ling+ga
NK008(nya)001:5805: mnan gal te 'grub par ma gyur na zhag gsum
NK008(nya)001:5806: bar du sngags bzlas nyin mtshan dkrug sgrol ging ar
NK008(nya)001:5808: shi sa bstan pa sngags kyi sa 'di'i mjug ma tshang lags /
NK008(nya)001:5809: dmar po'i rtags yig bzhugs so //
NK008(nya)001:5810: 'jam dpal dmar pos yang gsungs pa //
NK008(nya)001:5811: bsnyen sgrub las sbyor kun la yang //
NK008(nya)001:5812: rtags kyi rim pa bstan pa ni //
NK008(nya)001:5813: bsnyen pa dgug pa'i rtags dag ni //
NK008(nya)001:5814: rta pa dag ni mi shar dang //
NK008(nya)001:5815: mi dmar bya khra zhub can dang //
NK008(nya)001:5816: shan pa rngon pa khyi khrid dang //
NK008(nya)001:5817: 'od dang sgra la sogs pa dang //
NK008(nya)001:5818: thugs chom khang pa 'tshegs pa dang //
NK008(nya)001:5819: rtags rab mngon sum dag tu 'byung //
NK008(nya)001:5820: rtags byung phud tshogs gtang rag btang //
NK008(nya)001:5821: rbad pa dag ni rtags bstan pa //
NK008(nya)001:5822: rta la zhon nas rgyug pa dang //
NK008(nya)001:5823: dgra yi mtshon cha thob pa dang //
NK008(nya)001:5824: 'khrug pa'i ru bkod byed pa dang //
NK008(nya)001:5825: ra g.yag lug la sogs pa dang //
NK008(nya)001:5826: rta dang sha ba ri dwags rnams //
NK008(nya)001:5827: bzung ba'am khrid pa la sogs pa'o //
NK008(nya)001:5828: de ltar byung nas bsad pa brtsam //
NK008(nya)001:5829: bsad pa dag gi rtags bstan pa //
NK008(nya)001:5830: dang po bla khug rtags rnams 'byung //
NK008(nya)001:5831: ra g.yag ri dwags gong ltar 'byung //
NK008(nya)001:5833: gong gi ra g.yag la sogs pa //
NK008(nya)001:5834: rta lug mi la sogs pa dang //
NK008(nya)001:5835: sems can rnam pa gang yang rung //
NK008(nya)001:5836: bsad pa byung na las rnams 'grub //
NK008(nya)001:5837: shan pa'i tshogs la gtang rag btang //
NK008(nya)001:5838: bsad pa mi 'gyur rtags bstan pa //
NK008(nya)001:5839: bshas zin sha khrag khyer ba dang //
NK008(nya)001:5840: snying phyung mgo bcad nang rol bton //
NK008(nya)001:5841: dngos su khrid nas bshas pa 'am //
NK008(nya)001:5842: nyams sam rmi lam byung ba dang //
NK008(nya)001:5843: brtod la mnan te phur pas btab //
NK008(nya)001:5844: dmar po spu gri reg chod kyi rtags yig yin no //
NK008(nya)001:5845: dmar po'i rtags yig lugs gcig yin //
NK008(nya)001:5846: dang po la rtags 'di lta bu 'byung ngo //
NK008(nya)001:5847: dang po nyams dga' ba snyam byed pa dang /
NK008(nya)001:5848: lho phyogs kyi sgo phyed pa snyam byed pa dang /
NK008(nya)001:5849: shel gyi mchod rten la bskor ba byed pa snyam pa dang /
NK008(nya)001:5850: mi gcer bu chen po dag dga' ba'i gtam byed zer ba dang /
NK008(nya)001:5851: btsun pa'i tshul byung mang po gtam zer ba dang /
NK008(nya)001:5852: skad rigs mi gcig pa'i mi la mdza' bo brten pa dang /
NK008(nya)001:5853: slob dpon dus gtan du rmi ba dang /
NK008(nya)001:5854: mi reng dmar po chen po zhig /
NK008(nya)001:5855: bdag la mchod cing bskor ba byed pa dang //
NK008(nya)001:5856: stag dang seng+ge 'phyo zhing 'ong ba dang //
NK008(nya)001:5857: de rnams lha rtags kyi dod yin no //
NK008(nya)001:5858: dgra gsod rtags kyi mtshan ma 'di lta bu 'byung ste /
NK008(nya)001:5859: bdag gis sa brkos rtsa ba gting nas 'don pa dang /
NK008(nya)001:5860: rtsi zhing nags tshal chad pa dang //
NK008(nya)001:5861: ra bsad de snying phyung ba dang //
NK008(nya)001:5863: dgra'i yul mkhar bshig pa dang /
NK008(nya)001:5866: ban+d+he yin na rnga dang dril bu 'phrog pa dang /
NK008(nya)001:5867: skye bo yin na mda' dang gzhu dang mtshon cha 'phrog pa dang /
NK008(nya)001:5868: rgyal po yin na rke g.yu bcad pa dang //
NK008(nya)001:5870: de rnams byung na sod pa'i rtags yin no //
NK008(nya)001:5872: nang sngags rgyal po 'di sgrub na //
NK008(nya)001:5874: mgo la mchod rten skyes pa dang //
NK008(nya)001:5875: zhang blon mang po byung ba dang //
NK008(nya)001:5876: mon pa mang po byung ba ni //
NK008(nya)001:5877: sngags la 'khrugs pa med pa yin //
NK008(nya)001:5878: tsig tsig byed cing khro 'dod na //
NK008(nya)001:5879: las rnams myur du bstun la bya //
NK008(nya)001:5880: phyo phyo byed cing sha 'dod na //
NK008(nya)001:5881: thugs dam myur du bskang bar bya //
NK008(nya)001:5883: nyams dga' thugs dam bskang ba yin //
NK008(nya)001:5885: dgu pa bstan srung gi skor la /
NK008(nya)001:5886: dpe tshan drug tu yod pas /
NK008(nya)001:5887: de dag gter chen rin po che 'gyur me rdo
NK008(nya)001:5888: rje'i gsan yig ltar go rim dang tshan pa bcas
NK008(nya)001:5889: legs par bkod pa yin pas gshin rje 'i gshed
NK008(nya)001:5890: dmar po'i gzhung pod glegs bam yongs su rdzogs pa'i
NK008(nya)001:5891: dge bas rgyal ba'i bstan pa rin po che legs
NK008(nya)001:5892: par bsrung ba'i lcags ri chen po shog /
NK008(nya)001:5894: gshin rje dmar po phyi ltar du sgrub pa'i las byang dgra bgegs kyi srog 'phrog pa bzhugs so //
NK008(nya)001:5896: dpal phyag na rdo rje drag po 'dul ba la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK008(nya)001:5897: gshin rje dmar po phyi ltar du sgrub pa'i sngags la /
NK008(nya)001:5898: sgrol ging gi bdag po ma ru yab yum skyes bu chen pos lngas bskor te /
NK008(nya)001:5900: dang po kho nar shin tu gnas dben zhing nyams dga' bar /
NK008(nya)001:5901: rnal 'byor pa'i lta ba'i gdengs dang ldan zhing /
NK008(nya)001:5905: dus khyad par can drag po'i nyi ma la zhugs pa /
NK008(nya)001:5909: sgrub pa'i rdzas kyi yo byad /
NK008(nya)001:5910: drag po'i dgra bo'i rdzas la sogs pa bsag go //
NK008(nya)001:5911: de dang 'gras pa'i tshe dus bor la /
NK008(nya)001:5912: dur khrod kyi sa la dkyil 'khor byas la /
NK008(nya)001:5915: drag po rdzas kyi lnga la sogs pa bkod la /
NK008(nya)001:5916: phyi rol du gser skyems rgyas par btang /
NK008(nya)001:5917: snang srid kyi lha 'dre la dpang gzugs shing dmod bor ro //
NK008(nya)001:5918: de yang gtor ma'i lag len ni /
NK008(nya)001:5920: gyad la bshos bu gru gsum che ba gcig dbus su bzhag /
NK008(nya)001:5921: shar du srog bdag la gru bzhi gcig /
NK008(nya)001:5922: lhor tri se lag ring la gru gsum gcig /
NK008(nya)001:5923: nub tu khu le lag dgu la gru gsum gcig /
NK008(nya)001:5924: byang du yam shud dmar po la 'bras lug gcig /
NK008(nya)001:5925: yum la mdun du 'brang rgyas gcig /
NK008(nya)001:5926: shar lhor mtshams su mgar nag po la bzhos bu gru bzhi mkhar thabs gcig /
NK008(nya)001:5927: de la phud bran zhing ra ya kha gis bsregs sbyangs bkrus /
NK008(nya)001:5928: sngags drug phyag rgya drug gi byin gyis brlabs /
NK008(nya)001:5931: dzapa dang bstod pa yan chad rdzogs nas /
NK008(nya)001:5932: ma ru rtse'i gzhung bsrang ba ni /
NK008(nya)001:5933: dang po phyi nang gi chos thams cad mi dmigs pa las /
NK008(nya)001:5934: b+h+r+au zhes pas drag po'i gzhal yas khang /
NK008(nya)001:5935: thod pa dgu brtsegs kyi dgung mkhar /
NK008(nya)001:5936: mi ro dang rta ro'i khri brtsigs pa'i gdan steng /
NK008(nya)001:5937: mi ro dang rta ro gsar rnying mang po thang du brdal ba /
NK008(nya)001:5938: lce spyang khrag 'thung mang po khyi g.yab cing rgyug pa /
NK008(nya)001:5939: bya sha zan mang po lding ba /
NK008(nya)001:5941: gnam lcags kyii thog dang ser ba mang po 'bebs pa /
NK008(nya)001:5942: rnag khrag gi rba klong 'khrugs pa /
NK008(nya)001:5943: tshil zhag gi rgya mtsho 'khyil ba /
NK008(nya)001:5944: mi ro dang rta ro'i khri brtsegs pa'i gdan steng /
NK008(nya)001:5945: dbus su gru gsum mthing nag zla gam dmar po /
NK008(nya)001:5946: 'khor lo rtsibs lnga ba sgo 'khyud dang bcas pa bskyed /
NK008(nya)001:5947: ru tra dgra bgegs bsnol ba'i steng du /
NK008(nya)001:5949: de yongs su gyur pa las /
NK008(nya)001:5950: yak+sha g+h+ri yak+sha g+hi ba h'u /
NK008(nya)001:5952: sgrol ging bdag po ma ru rtse sku mdog dmar
NK008(nya)001:5953: po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa me'i mdog lta bu
NK008(nya)001:5954: / g.yas ral gri nam mkha' la phyar ba /
NK008(nya)001:5956: sku la ber dmar po gser ma gsol ba /
NK008(nya)001:5957: rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas dbu la rdzogs pa /
NK008(nya)001:5958: zhal gdangs mche gtsigs dgra bgegs zas su za ba /
NK008(nya)001:5959: sen mo lcags kyu lta bu la me 'bar ba /
NK008(nya)001:5960: smin ma dmar ser glog ltar 'khyug cing /
NK008(nya)001:5961: ral pa dmar ser sprin ltar du 'khrigs pa gcig bskyed do //
NK008(nya)001:5962: ging mo snying kha rag mo b+h+yo /
NK008(nya)001:5964: bdud mo gar kyi dbang phyug ma sku mdog smug
NK008(nya)001:5965: nag zhal gcig phyag gnyis ma g.yas pas sgrol ba'i
NK008(nya)001:5967: g.yon pas tsit+ta rol zhing thod khrag gtso bo la stob pa /
NK008(nya)001:5968: 'khor du ma bdud 'khor dang bcas pa gcig bskyed /
NK008(nya)001:5969: yab yum 'dril ba'i tshul du bskyed do //
NK008(nya)001:5970: gtso bo'i thugs ka nas tri lnga las gyad lnga bskyed de /
NK008(nya)001:5971: pa tra pa tra zhes pas shar phyogs su tshangs pa bskyed pa ni /
NK008(nya)001:5972: shar du srog bdag dung gi thor tshugs can sku mdog dkar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK008(nya)001:5973: g.yas pa gser gyi spu gri thogs pa /
NK008(nya)001:5974: g.yon pa g.yu yi lcags kyu thogs pa /
NK008(nya)001:5976: dbu la le brgan 'dzum thod gser gyis spras pa /
NK008(nya)001:5977: yas kyi mche gtsigs brang sub mtshams su slebs pa /
NK008(nya)001:5978: mas kyi mche gtsigs smin ma'i dkyil du sleb pa /
NK008(nya)001:5979: chibs su rta dkar po'am dmar po chibs pa /
NK008(nya)001:5980: sku la dar dkar ral ga gsol pa /
NK008(nya)001:5981: ma mchu dung sman chung dung gi khong lag can /
NK008(nya)001:5984: seng+ge dkar po'i thod ka can byas pa gcig bskyed do //
NK008(nya)001:5985: kro ta ni kro ta ni /
NK008(nya)001:5986: tro ta zhes mang du snang yang kro byas yod /
NK008(nya)001:5989: lho phyogs lcags mkhar sngon po'i nang du /
NK008(nya)001:5990: tri se lag ring sku mdog sngon po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK008(nya)001:5991: g.yas na shel gyi rdo rje /
NK008(nya)001:5992: g.yon na mi snying dmar po gsol ba zhal gdangs mche gtsigs rkan sgra sgrogs pa /
NK008(nya)001:5994: chibs su rta dkar po gzi mig can chibs pa /
NK008(nya)001:5995: the'u rang stong dang gshin rje 'khor gyis 'bum gyis bskor ba ba skyed /
NK008(nya)001:5996: d+ha sha g+h+ri ba d+ha sha g+h+ri ba sa ma ya dzah zhes pas /
NK008(nya)001:5997: nub phyogs bdud yul kha rag mgo dgu bdud kyi
NK008(nya)001:5998: zhing khams su khu le lag dgu sku mdog smug
NK008(nya)001:5999: po mchong gi mdog lta bu /
NK008(nya)001:6000: zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa g.yas pa na ral gri mkha' la 'phyar ba /
NK008(nya)001:6001: g.yon bas mi snying za ba /
NK008(nya)001:6002: zhal gdangs rkan sgra srid gsum g.yo ba /
NK008(nya)001:6003: mche ba gtsigs shing spyan rtsa dmar ba /
NK008(nya)001:6004: dbu skra kham nag gyen du bardzesa pa /
NK008(nya)001:6005: sog po lcags kyi sma ra yod pa /
NK008(nya)001:6006: chibs su bra nag rting dkar chibs pa /
NK008(nya)001:6007: 'khor du bdud sha za 'bum gyis bskor ba gcig bskyed /
NK008(nya)001:6010: byang phyogs gnod sbyin gyi zhing khams su /
NK008(nya)001:6011: bswe mkhar smug po'i nang du /
NK008(nya)001:6012: btsan rgod yam shud dmar po zhal gcig phyog gnyis pa g.yas na ba swe'i ldan dkar /
NK008(nya)001:6013: g.yon na bswe'i mda' gzhu thogs pa /
NK008(nya)001:6014: zhal gdangs rkan sgra sgrogs shing thog 'bebs pa /
NK008(nya)001:6015: mche gtsigs dgra bo la rngam zhing za ba /
NK008(nya)001:6016: dbu skra dmar nag rting bar slebs pa /
NK008(nya)001:6017: gnod sbyin zangs kyi rmog zhu gsol ba /
NK008(nya)001:6018: sku la dar dmar 'jol ber gsol ba /
NK008(nya)001:6019: chibs su zhu dmar rol po chibs pa /
NK008(nya)001:6020: 'khor du btsan dang gnod sbyin gyis bskor ba gcig bskyed /
NK008(nya)001:6021: shar lho the'u rang gi zhing khams su /
NK008(nya)001:6022: tri badz+ra sa d+hu sa ma ya /
NK008(nya)001:6024: dam can ma gar ba sku mdog smug nag zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
NK008(nya)001:6025: sku la dar nag gyi ber chen gsol ba /
NK008(nya)001:6026: gnam sa tsam gyi zhal gdangs pa /
NK008(nya)001:6027: gangs ri tsam gyi mche ba gtsigs pa /
NK008(nya)001:6028: glog dmar tsam gyi ljags brkyang ba /
NK008(nya)001:6029: zhal nas dug gi kha rlang 'phro ba /
NK008(nya)001:6030: dgra bo'i sha la za zhing khrag 'thung ba /
NK008(nya)001:6031: zhal nas rgyob dang sod kyi sgra sgrog pa /
NK008(nya)001:6032: sku la rin chen gser ka bcing ba /
NK008(nya)001:6033: zhabs la swag lham yu ring gsol ba /
NK008(nya)001:6034: dbu la 'bo zhu chen po gsol ba /
NK008(nya)001:6035: phyag g.yas gnam lcags tho chen bsnams pas log par blta ba'i mgo bo brdung ba /
NK008(nya)001:6036: g.yon pas las kyi rbud pa 'bud pas /
NK008(nya)001:6037: dgra khams thal ba'i rdul du rlog pa /
NK008(nya)001:6038: chibs su lcags spyang mgo dgu la chibs pa /
NK008(nya)001:6039: 'khor lha srin sde brgyad kyis bskor ba /
NK008(nya)001:6040: rol du lce spyang mang po khrid pa /
NK008(nya)001:6041: steng na bdud kyi bya nag 'thib pa gcig bskyed /
NK008(nya)001:6042: gzhan yang gsang ba'i gri thogs brgyad la sogs pa bsgom /
NK008(nya)001:6043: de nas rang nyid yi dam gyi ltar bskyed de
NK008(nya)001:6044: nga rgyal dang ldan par byas la snyan gsan dbab
NK008(nya)001:6047: phyogs phyogs dag ni ya gi na //
NK008(nya)001:6048: ri rab chen po'i zom rtse na //
NK008(nya)001:6049: de yi phyogs bzhi dbus dang lnga //
NK008(nya)001:6050: so so yi ni dgung mkhar nas //
NK008(nya)001:6051: bdud rje yi ni rgyal po drug /
NK008(nya)001:6052: bdud la gsang ba'i mtshan gsol ba //
NK008(nya)001:6053: skyes bu ging chen srog bdag drug /
NK008(nya)001:6054: skye 'gro'i srog la dbang sgyur zhing //
NK008(nya)001:6055: mi phyugs de ni gnyis kyi bdud //
NK008(nya)001:6056: dur khrod gnas mchog dam pa 'dir //
NK008(nya)001:6058: dam tshig dbang gis gshegs su gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6059: ya ma rak+sha hab sham sa ma ya dza dzah de nas spyan drangs pa ni /
NK008(nya)001:6061: dur khrod chen po'i gzhal yas nas //
NK008(nya)001:6062: thod pa dbu brtsegs sku mkhar nas //
NK008(nya)001:6063: srog bdag gnod sbyin ma ru rtse //
NK008(nya)001:6064: sku la 'khril ba'i yum gcig ma //
NK008(nya)001:6065: bdud mo gar gyi dbang phyug ma //
NK008(nya)001:6067: dur khrod gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6068: shar phyogs srin po'i zhing khams na //
NK008(nya)001:6069: dung dkar mkhar gyi nang shed nas //
NK008(nya)001:6070: tshangs pa'i rgyal po srin po'i gtso //
NK008(nya)001:6071: srog bdag g.yu'i smin ma can //
NK008(nya)001:6072: srog bdag ging phran 'bum dang bcas //
NK008(nya)001:6073: dur khrod gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6074: lho phyogs gshin rje'i zhing khams nas //
NK008(nya)001:6075: lcags mkhar sngon po sgo med na //
NK008(nya)001:6076: tri se lag ring gshin rje'i gtso //
NK008(nya)001:6077: nag po lcags kyi ral pa can //
NK008(nya)001:6078: gshin rje ging phran 'bum dang bcas //
NK008(nya)001:6079: dur khrod gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6080: nub phyogs bdud kyi zhing khams nas //
NK008(nya)001:6081: bdud yul kha rag mgo dgu nas //
NK008(nya)001:6082: khu le lag dgu bdud kyi gtso //
NK008(nya)001:6083: sog po lcags kyi sma ra can //
NK008(nya)001:6084: bdud po ging phran 'bum dang bcas //
NK008(nya)001:6085: dur khrod gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6086: byang phyogs gnod sbyin zhing khams nas //
NK008(nya)001:6087: bswe mkhar smug po'i nang shed na //
NK008(nya)001:6088: yam shud dmar po gnod sbyin gtso //
NK008(nya)001:6089: gnod sbyin zangs kyi rmog zhu can //
NK008(nya)001:6090: gnod sbyin ging phran 'bum dang bcas //
NK008(nya)001:6092: dur khrod gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6093: shar lho the'u rang zhing khams nas //
NK008(nya)001:6094: spre'u'i thod pa'i mkhar nang na //
NK008(nya)001:6095: mi skad de ni lhangs se lhang //
NK008(nya)001:6096: bya skad de ni lcongs se lcong //
NK008(nya)001:6097: spre'u skad ni rtsig ge rtsig /
NK008(nya)001:6098: the'u rang las la 'du ru ru //
NK008(nya)001:6099: the'u rang sprul pa cho dgu gtong //
NK008(nya)001:6100: de 'dra'i mkhar gyi nang shed na //
NK008(nya)001:6101: bdud rje legs pa the'u rang kun gyi gtso //
NK008(nya)001:6103: dur khrod gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6104: sprul pa'i ging chen bco brgyad yang //
NK008(nya)001:6106: dur khrod gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6107: +amo yak+sha g+h+ri ba yak+sha g+h+ri ba sa ma ya
NK008(nya)001:6108: dza dzah ging mo snying kha rak+mo sa ma ya
NK008(nya)001:6109: dzah pa tra pa tra kro ta ni kro ta
NK008(nya)001:6110: ni / d+ha sha g+h+ri ba d+ha sha g+h+ri ba /
NK008(nya)001:6111: shu la shu la tri badz+ra sa d+hu sa ma ya dzah h'u /
NK008(nya)001:6112: rol mo rnga gling sna tshogs dang //
NK008(nya)001:6113: dung dang pa wam gling bu'i sgra //
NK008(nya)001:6114: cha lang pheg rdob sil snyan sgra //
NK008(nya)001:6115: snyan pa'i sgra rnams phyogs bcur 'bul //
NK008(nya)001:6116: dkyil 'khor chen po'i 'khor lo 'bar ba'i rtsibs stengs su //
NK008(nya)001:6117: zhing chen bsnol ba'i gdan stengs su /
NK008(nya)001:6118: dar dang za 'og gdan stengs su //
NK008(nya)001:6119: skyes bu ging chen 'khor bcas rnams //
NK008(nya)001:6120: rim bzhin yangs par bzhugs su gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6121: ging ka ra sa ma ya tish+tha lhan /
NK008(nya)001:6122: de nas phyag btsal ba ni /
NK008(nya)001:6124: bdag nyid rnal 'byor dam tshig can //
NK008(nya)001:6125: khyod ni gsang ba'i sgrol ging tshogs //
NK008(nya)001:6126: mi 'da' ba yi phyag rgya dang //
NK008(nya)001:6127: dam tshig gzhung gis phyag 'tshal lo //
NK008(nya)001:6128: de nas sman byin gyis brlabs la mchod pa ni /
NK008(nya)001:6130: rang byung gdod nas dag pa ni //
NK008(nya)001:6131: rtsa brgyad stong la sbyar ba yi //
NK008(nya)001:6132: ra sa ya na la sogs pa'i //
NK008(nya)001:6133: dug lnga sel ba'i bdud rtsi'i mchog /
NK008(nya)001:6135: sgrol ging gnod sbyin dmar po dang //
NK008(nya)001:6136: bdud mo gar gyi dbang phyug la //
NK008(nya)001:6137: rnam dag bdud rtsi'i dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK008(nya)001:6138: bstan pa gnyan po bsrung phyir bzhes su gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6139: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK008(nya)001:6140: pra ma r+aa dza srin po'i gtso //
NK008(nya)001:6141: srin po ging phran 'bum bcas la //
NK008(nya)001:6142: rnam dag bdud rtsi'i dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK008(nya)001:6143: bstan pa gnyan po bsrung phyir bzhes su gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6144: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK008(nya)001:6145: tri se lag ring gshin rje'i gtso //
NK008(nya)001:6146: gshin rje ging phran 'bum bcas la //
NK008(nya)001:6147: rnam dag bdud rtsi'i dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK008(nya)001:6148: bstan pa gnyan po bsrung phyir bzhes su gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6149: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK008(nya)001:6150: khu le lag dgu bdud kyi gtso //
NK008(nya)001:6151: bdud po ging phran 'bum bcas la //
NK008(nya)001:6152: rnam dag bdud rtsi'i dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK008(nya)001:6153: bstan pa gnyan po bsrung phyir bzhes su gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6154: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK008(nya)001:6155: yam shud dmar po gnod sbyin gtso //
NK008(nya)001:6156: gnod sbyin ging phran 'bum bcas la //
NK008(nya)001:6157: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK008(nya)001:6158: bstan pa gnyan po bsrung phyir bzhes su gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6159: ma h+aa pany+tsa mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi //
NK008(nya)001:6160: shar lho the'u rang zhing khams nas //
NK008(nya)001:6161: mgar ba nag po bdud kyi gtso //
NK008(nya)001:6162: skye 'gro'i srog dbugs chen po la //
NK008(nya)001:6163: rnam dag bdud rtsi'i dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK008(nya)001:6164: bstan pa gnyan po bsrung phyir bzhes su gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6165: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK008(nya)001:6166: skye 'gro'i srog la dbang sgyur zhing //
NK008(nya)001:6167: dam nyams bsgral bar zhal bzhes pa'i //
NK008(nya)001:6169: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK008(nya)001:6170: bstan pa gnyan po bsrung phyir bzhes su gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6171: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK008(nya)001:6173: sngon gyi bskal pa dang po la //
NK008(nya)001:6174: ma la ya yi rtse mo ru //
NK008(nya)001:6175: phyag na rdo rje'i spyan snga ru //
NK008(nya)001:6176: gsang ba'i sgrol ging khyed rnams kyis //
NK008(nya)001:6177: bstan pa bsrung bar khas blangs nas //
NK008(nya)001:6178: srog gi snying po dngos su phul //
NK008(nya)001:6179: rdo rje ging chen du ni btags //
NK008(nya)001:6180: mi bsnyel phyir du rdo rje gtad //
NK008(nya)001:6181: dam tshig mchog las ma 'da' zhig /
NK008(nya)001:6182: ging ka ra sa ma la h'u /
NK008(nya)001:6184: nga ni phyag na rdo rje ste //
NK008(nya)001:6185: khyed ni gsang ba'i sgrol ging tshogs //
NK008(nya)001:6186: dam tshig nyams na bsreg byed pa'i //
NK008(nya)001:6188: 'chi ba med pa'i bdud rtsi'i chu //
NK008(nya)001:6189: dam tshig snying gi khrag chen po //
NK008(nya)001:6190: gal te dam tshig bka' 'das na //
NK008(nya)001:6191: lus ngag thal bar gyur ta re //
NK008(nya)001:6193: bdag kyang lha ru khyod mchod kyi //
NK008(nya)001:6194: khyod kyang dam las 'da' re kan //
NK008(nya)001:6195: bdag gi bu smad 'khor bcas kyi //
NK008(nya)001:6196: srog dang srid la mnga' ma mdzad //
NK008(nya)001:6198: khyod kyang dam las ma 'da' zhig /
NK008(nya)001:6199: ci bcol yed par dam chos shig /
NK008(nya)001:6201: ma h+aa rak+ta man+da la zhes srog snying dang bcas pa bgrang zhing /
NK008(nya)001:6203: de nas bachoda pa 'bul ba ni /
NK008(nya)001:6205: skyes bu ging chen 'khor bcas la //
NK008(nya)001:6206: phyi yi mchod pa 'bul ba ni //
NK008(nya)001:6207: mang yul stod kyi sman dang spos //
NK008(nya)001:6208: mang yul stod kyi rtsod dang zhun //
NK008(nya)001:6209: lho brag smad kyi ras dang rdzas //
NK008(nya)001:6210: rgya yul gting gi dar dang zab //
NK008(nya)001:6211: bal yul mthil gi sngo dang nags //
NK008(nya)001:6212: bod yul dbus kyi gser dang dngul //
NK008(nya)001:6213: byi ru mtshal dang ba bla gser //
NK008(nya)001:6214: dar sna thod dkar za 'og ras //
NK008(nya)001:6215: ka ra bu ram sbrang rtsi dang //
NK008(nya)001:6216: nya sha sgog btsong la phug tsh+wa //
NK008(nya)001:6217: 'bras dang khur ba sgo nga dang //
NK008(nya)001:6218: star kha ku sha rgun 'brum dang //
NK008(nya)001:6219: zho dang 'o ma mar dang thud //
NK008(nya)001:6220: mthun pa'i zhal zas sna tshogs kyi //
NK008(nya)001:6221: phyi yi mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6222: nang gi mchod pa 'bul ba ni //
NK008(nya)001:6223: btsos pa'i chang dang bsreg pa'i gsur //
NK008(nya)001:6224: bsad pa'i sha dang myos pa'i chang //
NK008(nya)001:6225: glo snying nang rol mkhal ma dang //
NK008(nya)001:6226: sna mig dbang po rna lce 'bras //
NK008(nya)001:6227: nang gi mchod par bzhes su gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6228: gsang ba'i mchod pa 'bul ba ni //
NK008(nya)001:6229: sman phud rak+ta gtor ma dang //
NK008(nya)001:6230: mthun pa'i dam rdzas bshos bzang dang //
NK008(nya)001:6231: tsa ra sme lug 'dab chags kyi //
NK008(nya)001:6232: snying sna srog dbugs mdangs dang rgyu //
NK008(nya)001:6233: gsang ba'i mchod par bzhes su gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6234: de nas gser skyems kyi mchod pa 'bul ba ni /
NK008(nya)001:6236: 'dzam bu gling gi zas kyi bcud //
NK008(nya)001:6237: nas chang gro chang 'bras chang rgun chang rin chen gser sbyar nas //
NK008(nya)001:6238: yon tan ma lus rdzogs pa'i lha //
NK008(nya)001:6239: sgrol ging sku mchog ma ru rtse //
NK008(nya)001:6240: sku la 'khril ba'i yum gcig ma //
NK008(nya)001:6241: bdud mo gar gyi dbang phyug ma //
NK008(nya)001:6243: mgul du 'don no zhal du gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6244: 'khor srungs ga nas skyongs bsam pa sgrubs //
NK008(nya)001:6245: sdang ba'i dgra la rtags phyungs shig /
NK008(nya)001:6246: pra ma r+aa dza srin po'i gtso //
NK008(nya)001:6247: sku sprul ging chen 'khor bcas la //
NK008(nya)001:6249: mgul du 'don no zhal du gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6250: 'khor srungs gnas skyongs bsam pa sgrubs //
NK008(nya)001:6251: sdang ba'i dgra la rtags phyungs shig /
NK008(nya)001:6252: tri se lag ring gshin rje'i gtso //
NK008(nya)001:6253: yon tan sprul pa 'khor bcas la //
NK008(nya)001:6255: mgul du 'don no zhal du gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6256: 'khor srungs rkyen bzlog bsam pa sgrubs //
NK008(nya)001:6257: sdang ba'i dgra la rtags phyungs shig /
NK008(nya)001:6258: d+ha sha g+h+ri ba bdud kyi gtso //
NK008(nya)001:6259: thugs sprul ging chen 'khor bcas la //
NK008(nya)001:6261: mgul du 'don no zhal du gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6262: 'khor srungs gnas skyongs bsam pa sgrubs //
NK008(nya)001:6263: sdang ba'i dgra la rtags phyungs shig /
NK008(nya)001:6264: d+ha sha gli ba gnod sbyin gtso //
NK008(nya)001:6265: gsung sprul ging chen 'khor bcas la //
NK008(nya)001:6267: mgul du 'don no zhal du gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6268: 'khor srungs gnas skyongs bsam pa sgrub //
NK008(nya)001:6269: sdang ba'i dgra la rtags phyungs shig /
NK008(nya)001:6270: rdo rje legs pa the'u rang gtso //
NK008(nya)001:6271: phrin las sprul pa 'khor bcas la //
NK008(nya)001:6273: mgul du 'don no zhal du gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6274: 'khor srungs gnas skyongs bsam pa sgrubs //
NK008(nya)001:6275: sdang ba'i dgra la rtag phyungs shig /
NK008(nya)001:6276: sprul pa'i gri thogs bco brgyad la //
NK008(nya)001:6278: mgul du 'don no zhal du gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6279: 'khor srungs gnas skyongs bsam pa sgrubs //
NK008(nya)001:6280: sdang ba'i dgra la rtags phyungs shig /
NK008(nya)001:6282: skye 'gro'i srog la mnga' mdzad dbugs la dbang bsgyur ba'i //
NK008(nya)001:6283: sha khrag rus la longs spyod cing //
NK008(nya)001:6284: 'jig rten las la dbang sgyur ba'i //
NK008(nya)001:6285: sgrol ging bdag po ma ru rtse //
NK008(nya)001:6286: yab yum 'khor gyi gyad chen lnga //
NK008(nya)001:6287: sprul pa sgrol ging 'bum dang bcas pa dgongs su gsol /
NK008(nya)001:6289: sngon gyi bskal pa dang po la //
NK008(nya)001:6290: ri bo gnam lcags ma la ya //
NK008(nya)001:6291: drag shul can gyi rtse mo la //
NK008(nya)001:6292: gnyen po stobs kyi lha dpal phyag na rdo rje 'chang dang /
NK008(nya)001:6293: dam can thams cad dbang du bsdu zhing dam la 'dogs pa'i lha mchog ya m+aan+ta ka'i spyan sngar /
NK008(nya)001:6294: gsang ba'i sgrol ging chen po khyed rnams kyis srog
NK008(nya)001:6295: gi snying po phul nas bstan pa bsrung bar khas
NK008(nya)001:6296: blangs / skye 'gro'i srog la dbang sgyur /
NK008(nya)001:6299: lce la bdud rtsi bzhag nas dbang du bsdus /
NK008(nya)001:6300: dam la btags nas sgrol ging bya bar khas blangs /
NK008(nya)001:6301: brag phug lha zhal dgra 'dul du slob dpon a
NK008(nya)001:6302: bu si ti'i spyan sngar khas blangs dam bcas pa'o
NK008(nya)001:6303: // mang yul gyi byams sprin gyi lha khang du
NK008(nya)001:6304: slob dpon pad+ma 'byung gnas kyi spyan sngar khas blangs
NK008(nya)001:6305: zhing dam bcas pa bzhin du /
NK008(nya)001:6306: dam las ma 'da' bstan pa gnyan po srungs //
NK008(nya)001:6307: bdag gis dngos su 'byor pa'i mchod pa phyi nang
NK008(nya)001:6308: gsang ba'i dam rdzas yid sprul pa la sogs pa
NK008(nya)001:6309: 'bul gyis thugs dam bskang bar gyur cig /
NK008(nya)001:6310: rnal 'byor bdag gi rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig chag nyams zhig ral du gyur pa /
NK008(nya)001:6311: rdzas dang yo byad ma tshang ba /
NK008(nya)001:6312: bsnyen sgrub lo zlar lus pa /
NK008(nya)001:6313: mchod pa dus las yol ba dang /
NK008(nya)001:6314: phud la gtsang sbra ma byed pa la sogs le lo dang snyoms las su gyur pa dang /
NK008(nya)001:6315: gzhung las 'gal zhing thugs da nga mi mthun pa rnams mthol zhing bshags so //
NK008(nya)001:6316: rnal 'byor pa bdag tshe ring ba dang /
NK008(nya)001:6319: mthu dang bkrag dang gzi brjid la logs pa'i dngos grub rtsol cig /
NK008(nya)001:6321: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa bshig pa /
NK008(nya)001:6322: dkon mchog gi dbu 'phang dmod pa /
NK008(nya)001:6328: lan pa med par srog la rgol ba /
NK008(nya)001:6329: bsngo ba med par nor la 'bags pa /
NK008(nya)001:6330: mthu bu lon ltar du snyegs pa 'di /
NK008(nya)001:6331: nam mkha' stong pa la tshad ma bzung /
NK008(nya)001:6332: rgya mtsho lta bu la gting ma dpag /
NK008(nya)001:6333: bye ri la grangs ma bzung /
NK008(nya)001:6334: las dang rnam smin la snyad ma btags /
NK008(nya)001:6335: mi rjes la dgra ru ma bcug /
NK008(nya)001:6337: tshe yi 'du byed myur du skums shig /
NK008(nya)001:6339: sa yi rten phur thon cig /
NK008(nya)001:6340: rgyab rten lha dang myur du phyes //
NK008(nya)001:6341: mdza' ba kun dang phrol la shog cig /
NK008(nya)001:6342: phyungs shig rgya 'dre slong la shog cig /
NK008(nya)001:6343: las kyi rlung gis rgyab nas ded //
NK008(nya)001:6344: mun pa nag po'i mdun nas bsus //
NK008(nya)001:6345: gshin rje'i pho nyas snying nas drongs //
NK008(nya)001:6346: tshogs bdag glang snyas g.yas nas phyungs //
NK008(nya)001:6347: ta ki r+aa dzas g.yon nas phyungs //
NK008(nya)001:6348: mche ba can gyi klad nas phul //
NK008(nya)001:6349: sder bzhi can gyis snying nas drongs shig /
NK008(nya)001:6350: ces drang srong gi dmod pa gdab bo //
NK008(nya)001:6352: de nas snga dro nyi ma'i zer dang /
NK008(nya)001:6353: dgong mo zla ba'i zer la drag tu bskul lo //
NK008(nya)001:6354: gshin rje dmar po phyi ltar du bsgrub pa'i las byang rdzogs so //
NK008(nya)001:6355: 'jam dpal dmar po gnod sbyin brgyad dang /
NK008(nya)001:6356: bka' ma chog sgrig na'ang 'di mkho /
NK008(nya)001:6357: ging chen bzhi bka' nyan 'khor dang bcas pa'i rgyun gtor bzhugs so //
NK008(nya)001:6358: sgrol ging dmar po la gtor ma 'bul bar 'dod na /
NK008(nya)001:6360: thog mar yi dam gyi bsnyen sgrub dang tshogs rgyas par byas nas /
NK008(nya)001:6362: stong pa'i ngang las ya las rlung /
NK008(nya)001:6364: ka las mi mgo'i sgyed pu gsum gyi steng du /
NK008(nya)001:6365: +aahls thod pa yangs shing rgya che ba'i nang du /
NK008(nya)001:6366: gtor ma dgra bgegs bsgral ba'i sha khrag bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho chen por gyur /
NK008(nya)001:6367: b+h+r+aa bi shwa bi shud+d+he b+han+d+ha ny+dz+aa na tsakra b+h+r+au /
NK008(nya)001:6369: gzhal yas khang 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi /
NK008(nya)001:6370: dbus gru gsum mthing nag 'bar ba'i nang du /
NK008(nya)001:6371: thod mkhar chen po brtsegs pa'i gzhal yas khang gi dbus su /
NK008(nya)001:6372: zhing bcu dgra bgegs pho mo bsnol ba'i steng du /
NK008(nya)001:6375: sgrol ging gi bdag po ma ru rtse /
NK008(nya)001:6376: sku mdog dmar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa zhal gdangs shing mche ba gtsigs pa /
NK008(nya)001:6377: sku la dar gyi ber dmar po gser gyi rgyan thogs pa gsol ba /
NK008(nya)001:6378: gser ka rin po che'i ske rags bcings shing /
NK008(nya)001:6379: phyag g.yas pas gnam lcags kyi ral gri me 'bar ba nam mkha' la 'phyar zhing /
NK008(nya)001:6380: dgra bo'i srog rtsa nyal nyal gcod pa /
NK008(nya)001:6381: g.yon pas dgra bgegs kyi tsit+ta gsol ba /
NK008(nya)001:6382: sen mo lcags kyu lta bu la me 'bar bas dgra bgegs zas su za ba /
NK008(nya)001:6384: ging mo snying kha rak+mo b+h+yo /
NK008(nya)001:6385: zhes pas yum bdud mo gar gyi dbang phyug ma sku mdog smug nag zhal gcig phyag gnyis ma /
NK008(nya)001:6386: g.yas gri gug yab la 'khyud pa /
NK008(nya)001:6387: g.yon pas thod pa khrag gis bkang ba yab la stob pa /
NK008(nya)001:6388: dbu skra ral pa mun ltar gtibs pa'o //
NK008(nya)001:6389: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa la tri tri tri tri las /
NK008(nya)001:6390: shar du pra ma r+aa dzah lhor tri se lag ring /
NK008(nya)001:6391: nub tu khu le lag dgu /
NK008(nya)001:6392: byang du yam shud dmar po /
NK008(nya)001:6393: sprul pa'i gri thogs bco brgyad /
NK008(nya)001:6394: ging chen rdo rje legs pa rnams bzhugs par byur /
NK008(nya)001:6397: phyogs phyogs de ni pha gi na //
NK008(nya)001:6398: ri rab chen po'i zom rtse na //
NK008(nya)001:6399: de yi phyogs bzhi dbus dang lnga //
NK008(nya)001:6400: so so yi ni sku mkhar na //
NK008(nya)001:6401: bdud chen gyi ni rgyal po lnga //
NK008(nya)001:6402: bdud la gsang ba'i mtshan gsol ba //
NK008(nya)001:6403: skyes bu'i ging chen srog bdag lnga //
NK008(nya)001:6405: dam tshig dbang gis gshegs su gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6407: ging mi snying kha rag mo b+h+yo /
NK008(nya)001:6410: d+ha sha g+hi ba d+ha sha g+h+ri ba /
NK008(nya)001:6412: badz+ra sa d+h+au sa ma ya dza dzah b+h+yo /
NK008(nya)001:6413: phyogs phyogs de ni pha gi na //
NK008(nya)001:6414: mi ro mang po'i lding khang na //
NK008(nya)001:6415: thod pa dgu brtsegs dgung mkhar na //
NK008(nya)001:6416: srog bdag gnod sbyin ma ru rtse //
NK008(nya)001:6417: sku la 'khril ba'i yum gcig ma //
NK008(nya)001:6418: bdud mo gar gyi dbang phyug ma //
NK008(nya)001:6420: dam tshig dbang gis gshegs su gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6421: nyi ma shar phyogs pha gi na //
NK008(nya)001:6422: shar phyogs srin po'i yul khams na //
NK008(nya)001:6423: pra ma r+aa dza srin po'i bdag /
NK008(nya)001:6424: srin po'i ging phran 'bum dang bcas //
NK008(nya)001:6426: dam tshig dbang gis gshegs su gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6427: nyi ma lho phyogs gshin rje'i zhing khams na //
NK008(nya)001:6428: tri se lag rig gshin rje'i gtso //
NK008(nya)001:6429: gshin rje ging phran 'bum dang bcas //
NK008(nya)001:6431: dam tshig dbang gis gshegs su gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6432: nyi ma nub phyogs gshin rje'i zhing khams na //
NK008(nya)001:6433: nub phyogs bdud kyi yul rtse nas //
NK008(nya)001:6434: khu le lag dgu bdud kyi gtso //
NK008(nya)001:6435: bdud po kyi ging phran 'bum dang bcas //
NK008(nya)001:6437: dam tshig dbang gis gshegs su gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6438: nyi ma byang phyogs pha gi na //
NK008(nya)001:6439: btsan yul zangs thang dmar po nas //
NK008(nya)001:6440: yam shud dmar po btsan gyi gtso //
NK008(nya)001:6441: btsan po ging phran 'bum dang bcas //
NK008(nya)001:6443: dam tshig dbang gis gshegs su gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6444: sprul pa'i gri thogs bco brgyad dang //
NK008(nya)001:6445: ging chen rdo rje legs pa rnams //
NK008(nya)001:6447: dam tshig dbang gis gshegs su gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6448: khyed ni sgrol ging chen po ste //
NK008(nya)001:6449: 'jam dpal gshin rje'i bka' nyan mchog /
NK008(nya)001:6450: mi 'da' ba yi phyag rgya can //
NK008(nya)001:6451: dam tshig dbang gis phyag 'tshal lo //
NK008(nya)001:6453: ging mi snying kha la rag mo b+h+yo /
NK008(nya)001:6456: d+ha sha g+hi ba d+ha sha g+h+ri ba /
NK008(nya)001:6458: badz+ra sa d+h+au sa ma ya ma h+aa ba ling ta kh+aa hi /
NK008(nya)001:6461: ma h+aa go ro tsa na la kh+aa hi /
NK008(nya)001:6462: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK008(nya)001:6463: zhes pa gsum mam bdun gyis bar la dbul lo //
NK008(nya)001:6464: hoh sgrol ging bdag po ma ru rtse dpon g.yog 'khor dang bcas pas /
NK008(nya)001:6465: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa dar ba /
NK008(nya)001:6466: sems can la bde skyid 'byung ba dang /
NK008(nya)001:6467: rnal 'byor pa'i bsam pa yid bzhin du 'grub par mdzad du gsol /
NK008(nya)001:6469: gtor ma ru mtshon mdun du mchod //
NK008(nya)001:6470: rgya gar d+ha na da las rgyun gyi thugs dam ma chags par mdzad gsung bar gda' lags /
NK008(nya)001:6471: gnod sbyin brgyad la chos tshan bzhi yod gsungs par gda' lags /
NK008(nya)001:6472: ma ru rtse phyi chos skyong ging ltar du sgrub
NK008(nya)001:6473: pa'i skong gso skong bshags dang bcas pa bzhugs so
NK008(nya)001:6474: // 'jam dpal gshin rje ma ru rtse chos skyong gi tshul du sgrub pa la /
NK008(nya)001:6475: de'i dbang dang bsnyen pa song ba /
NK008(nya)001:6477: rang nyid yi dam gshin rje'am phyag rdor gang rung gi phrin las byas rjes /
NK008(nya)001:6478: +amo swa b+h+aa wa shud+d+ha barba d+ha r+m+aaswa b+h+aa wa shud+d+ho&aham /
NK008(nya)001:6480: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+au las rin po che'i sa gzhi dmar po yangs shing rgya che ba /
NK008(nya)001:6481: 'khor yug thams cad zangs ri dmar po 'dra ba /
NK008(nya)001:6488: mi mgo dang thod pa sna tshogs bshug glu len pa /
NK008(nya)001:6489: sa gzhi la spu gri dang mdung rtse la sogs pa'i mtshon cha sna tshogs skyes pa /
NK008(nya)001:6490: bar snang la 'khor lo dang tri shu la sogs ba'i char 'bab pa /
NK008(nya)001:6491: sa gzhi la 'tshubs pa'i me lce sna tshogs 'khrugs pa /
NK008(nya)001:6495: mi ro dang rta ro la sogs pa'i thod pa
NK008(nya)001:6496: dgu rtsegs dgung mkhar chen po gru bzhi sgo bzhi
NK008(nya)001:6497: pa / de'i dbus su gru gsum dmar nag zla
NK008(nya)001:6498: gam dmar po'i phyi rim la 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi
NK008(nya)001:6500: shar du dung mkhar dkar po /
NK008(nya)001:6502: nub tu bdud mkhar nag po /
NK008(nya)001:6503: byang du zangs mkhar dmar po /
NK008(nya)001:6504: dbus su bswe mkhar smug po /
NK008(nya)001:6505: phyi bswe mkhar smug po sgo rnams zangs dang them skas byi ru dmar pos byas pa /
NK008(nya)001:6506: g.yu dang ra gan gyi ru bzhi /
NK008(nya)001:6508: mi mgo skam rlon gyi ba gam sum btsegs /
NK008(nya)001:6509: nyi zla dang gza' skar gyi 'od gsal ba /
NK008(nya)001:6510: rgya che la dpang mtho ba /
NK008(nya)001:6511: dbus kyi thod mkhar dang phyogs bzhi rnams snying gi tog dang mi ro'i rgyal mtshan /
NK008(nya)001:6512: dar dmar gyi ru mtshon 'brug sgra drag tu sgrog pa /
NK008(nya)001:6513: gnam lcags kyi thog dang ser ba 'bab pa /
NK008(nya)001:6514: bar snang la bswe bya khra dang srin bya 'ug
NK008(nya)001:6515: pa la sogs pa'i ltas ngan gyi bya mang po
NK008(nya)001:6516: 'thab cing gshog pa 'debs shing rkan sgra sgrog pa
NK008(nya)001:6517: / sa gzhi thams cad me 'tshubs shing 'khyil ba 'khrugs pa'i klong na /
NK008(nya)001:6518: mi ro dang rta ro mang po khal du bkal zhing /
NK008(nya)001:6519: mi khrag dang rta khrag rgya mtshor 'khyil ba'i klong na /
NK008(nya)001:6520: ro langs gar byed cing 'byung pos khu 'debs pa
NK008(nya)001:6521: keng rus gad mo rgod cing sha zas ngur sgra
NK008(nya)001:6522: sgrog pa / gzhan yang dreng mo lag pa gdengs shing /
NK008(nya)001:6523: 'phar bas rkan sgra brdeb pa la sogs pa /
NK008(nya)001:6524: dur khrod kyi gcan gzan mang po sha la dga' zhing khrag la rngams pa /
NK008(nya)001:6525: phyi rol du rgyug shing 'jigs pa dang /
NK008(nya)001:6527: 'jigs pa'i dur khrod chen pos bskor ba'i gzhal yas
NK008(nya)001:6528: khang gi steng gi nam mkha' la g.yang gzhi'i bla
NK008(nya)001:6529: bre dang / rgyu rlon gyi lda ldi dang mi
NK008(nya)001:6530: ro dang rta ro mang po bar snang la lding
NK008(nya)001:6531: bre dang / zhing / logs thams cad khrag dron mos byug pa'i nang thod mkhar gyi dbus su /
NK008(nya)001:6532: pad+ma dang nyi ma mi ro dang rta ro dgra
NK008(nya)001:6533: bgegs bsnol ba'i steng du yi ge h+r+aihdamara po las
NK008(nya)001:6534: 'od zer 'phros / bstan pa bshig pa'i dgra bgegs
NK008(nya)001:6535: gdug pa can thams cad tshar bcad tshur 'dus yongs
NK008(nya)001:6537: yak+sha g+h+ri ba h+aum zhes pas srog bdag chen po
NK008(nya)001:6538: gnod sbyin ma ru rtse sku mdog dmar po zhal
NK008(nya)001:6540: phyag g.yas gnam lcags kyi ral gri me 'bar ba nam mkha' la 'phyar zhing /
NK008(nya)001:6541: g.yon pas dgra bgegs kyi snying srog rtsa dang bcas pa zhal du gsol ba /
NK008(nya)001:6542: sku la zab ber dmar po gser gyi pa tas brgyan pa gsol ba /
NK008(nya)001:6543: thod pa skam po lngas dbu brgyan dang /
NK008(nya)001:6544: rlan pa khrag 'dzag pa lnga bcu'i do shal 'phyang ba /
NK008(nya)001:6546: mche ba bzhi rab tu gtsigs pa /
NK008(nya)001:6547: spyan gsum dmar la zlum pa /
NK008(nya)001:6548: smin ma dang sma ra dmar ser du 'khrugs pa /
NK008(nya)001:6549: dbu skra dmar nag sprin ltar gtibs shing rting par slebs pa /
NK008(nya)001:6550: sen mo lcags kyu lta bur me 'bar bas /
NK008(nya)001:6551: dgra bgegs kyi sha la za ba /
NK008(nya)001:6552: rab tu khro zhing shin tu rngams pa'i cha lugs can /
NK008(nya)001:6554: g.yon brkyang ba'i gar stabs kyi bzhugs pa /
NK008(nya)001:6555: dregs pa lha srin sde brgyad bran du 'khol ba'o //
NK008(nya)001:6556: de'i g.yon du ging mo snying kha rag mo b+h+yo /
NK008(nya)001:6558: yum bdud mo gar gyi dbang phyug ma sku mdog smug nag zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK008(nya)001:6559: phyag g.yas dgra bgegs sgrol ba'i gri gug 'phyar zhing /
NK008(nya)001:6560: g.yon tsit+ta la rol zhing thod khrag gtso la stob pa /
NK008(nya)001:6561: zhal bgrad cing mche ba gtsigs pa //
NK008(nya)001:6562: ljags 'dril zhing rkan sgra brdeb pa /
NK008(nya)001:6563: ma mo'i bshugs glu len pa /
NK008(nya)001:6564: 'khor du ma bdud 'bum gyis bskor ba'o //
NK008(nya)001:6565: gtso bo'i thugs ka nas tri bzhi 'phros pa las /
NK008(nya)001:6568: shar du srog bdag tshangs pa dung gi thor tshugs
NK008(nya)001:6569: can sku mdog dkar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa
NK008(nya)001:6570: / g.yas zangs gri 'phyar bas dgra bgegs kyi srog rtsa gcod pa /
NK008(nya)001:6575: dbu le brgan gyi 'dzum thod gser gyi spras pas brgyan pa /
NK008(nya)001:6576: yas kyi mche ba brang gi lhen snar sleb pa /
NK008(nya)001:6577: mas kyi mche gtsigs smin ma'i dbus su sleb pa /
NK008(nya)001:6578: sku la dar dkar gyi na bza' gsol ba /
NK008(nya)001:6579: sman chung dung gi khong lag can /
NK008(nya)001:6580: seng ge dkar mo'i thod kha byas pa gsol ba /
NK008(nya)001:6581: chibs su rta dkar phrum dmar la chibs pa /
NK008(nya)001:6583: pa tra pa tra zhes pas lhor tri se lag
NK008(nya)001:6584: ring sku mdog sngon po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa
NK008(nya)001:6585: / g.yas shel gyi rdo rje rtse lnga pa 'phyar bas dgra bgegs rdul du rlog pa /
NK008(nya)001:6586: g.yon pas mi snying dmar po gsol ba /
NK008(nya)001:6587: zhal gdangs shing mche ba gtsigs pa /
NK008(nya)001:6588: rkan sgra brdeb pas dgra bo khram la 'debs pa /
NK008(nya)001:6589: chibs su rta dkar gzi mig la chibs pa /
NK008(nya)001:6590: 'khor du the'u rang dang gshin rje 'bum gyis bskor ba'o //
NK008(nya)001:6591: d+ha sha g+h+ri ba d+ha sha g+h+ri ba zhes pas /
NK008(nya)001:6592: nub tu bdud po khu le lag dgu sku mdog smug po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK008(nya)001:6593: g.yas ral gri rgya gram 'phyar zhing /
NK008(nya)001:6594: g.yon mi snying dmar po za ba /
NK008(nya)001:6595: zhal gdangs mche ba gtsigs pa /
NK008(nya)001:6596: rkan sgra tog pas srid gsum g.yo ba /
NK008(nya)001:6598: dbu skra kham nag thod pas brgyan pa /
NK008(nya)001:6599: sog po lcags kyi sma ra can /
NK008(nya)001:6600: chibs su bdud rta nag po rting dkar la chibs pa /
NK008(nya)001:6601: 'khor du sha za dang bdud dmag 'bum gyis bskor ba'o //
NK008(nya)001:6602: shu la shu la zhes pas /
NK008(nya)001:6603: byang du ya ma shud dmar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK008(nya)001:6606: zhal gdangs shing mche ba gtsigs pa /
NK008(nya)001:6607: rkan sgra brdebs pas thog dang ser ba 'bebs pa /
NK008(nya)001:6608: dbu skra dmar nag rting par sleb pa /
NK008(nya)001:6609: sku la bswe khrab dmar po gsol zhing /
NK008(nya)001:6610: dbu la zangs kyi rmog zhu gsol pa /
NK008(nya)001:6612: chibs su gyi ling dmar po la chibs pa /
NK008(nya)001:6613: 'khor du btsan dang gnod sbyin 'bum gyis bskor ba'o //
NK008(nya)001:6614: bar khyams la gri thogs kyi sgrol ging bco brgyad /
NK008(nya)001:6616: sku mdog dmar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK008(nya)001:6617: sku la g.yang gzhi dang bswe khrab dmar po gsol ba /
NK008(nya)001:6618: phyag na ral gri dang bswe mdung dang mda' gzhu sogs pa'i mtshon cha sna tshogs bsnams shing /
NK008(nya)001:6619: dgra bgegs sgrol ba'i las la brtson pa /
NK008(nya)001:6620: thod skam dang mi mgo'i phreng bas brgyan pa /
NK008(nya)001:6621: ral pa kham nag rgyab tu bcings pa /
NK008(nya)001:6622: dgra bo'i srog dbugs leg cing phyogs bcur rgyug pa /
NK008(nya)001:6623: chibs su gyi ling dmar po dang /
NK008(nya)001:6624: bswe yi bya khra dang g.yag kham pa la chibs pa /
NK008(nya)001:6625: 'khor shan pa bye ba sa yas bskor ba /
NK008(nya)001:6626: thod mkhar gyi nang sgo srung ba shwa na ma
NK008(nya)001:6627: dmar mo dgra la za ba 'jigs pa'i nga ro
NK008(nya)001:6628: sgrog pa / phyi sgo na zangs kyi srin mo
NK008(nya)001:6629: mche ba bzhi btsigs pa re res mi ro bzung
NK008(nya)001:6631: phyi'i khor yug dmar po la khram thogs kyi bdud pho /
NK008(nya)001:6636: ma gshin bye ba sa ya 'bum sde /
NK008(nya)001:6637: las byed drug khri drug stong /
NK008(nya)001:6638: dregs pa lha srin sde brgyad /
NK008(nya)001:6639: dge bsnyen rdo rje legs pa sku mdog sna tshogs pa /
NK008(nya)001:6642: mi sdug pa'i sgra skad sna tshogs sgrog pa /
NK008(nya)001:6643: lag na mi sdug pa'i mtshon cha sna tshogs thogs
NK008(nya)001:6644: nas gnod byed dgra bgegs thams cad skad cig nyid
NK008(nya)001:6645: la tshar gcod pa'i skyes bu /
NK008(nya)001:6647: dam can rgya mtsho dpag tu med pas bskor ba'o //
NK008(nya)001:6648: gtso 'khor de rnams kyi spyi bor +amo /
NK008(nya)001:6650: thugs ka'i h'u las 'od zer 'phros pas byang shar
NK008(nya)001:6651: ma ru rtse'i dur khrod nas sgrub cing mchod pa'i
NK008(nya)001:6652: gnas 'dir badz+ra ma ya dzahdzah kyee /
NK008(nya)001:6653: phyogs phyogs de ni pha ki na //
NK008(nya)001:6654: ri rab chen po'i zom rtse nas //
NK008(nya)001:6655: de yi phyogs bzhi dbus dang lnga //
NK008(nya)001:6656: bswe mkhar dmar po'i nang shed na //
NK008(nya)001:6657: bdud rje de ni rgyal po lnga //
NK008(nya)001:6658: bdud la gsang ba'i mtshan gsol ba //
NK008(nya)001:6659: skyes bu ging chen srog bdud lnga //
NK008(nya)001:6660: skye 'gro'i srog la dbang sgyur zhing //
NK008(nya)001:6661: mi phyugs de ni gnyis kyi bdud //
NK008(nya)001:6662: dur khrod chen po'i gnas mchog nas //
NK008(nya)001:6663: de ring rnal 'byor ba dag 'bod na //
NK008(nya)001:6664: dam tshig dbang gis gshegs su gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6665: sa ma ya rak+sha ham sham sa ma ya dza dzah h'u /
NK008(nya)001:6666: dur khrod chen po'i gzhal yas nas //
NK008(nya)001:6667: mi ro mang po'i lding khang nas //
NK008(nya)001:6668: thod pa dgu brtsegs sku mkhar nas //
NK008(nya)001:6669: srog bdag gnod sbyin ma ru rtse //
NK008(nya)001:6670: sku la 'khril ba'i yum gcig ma //
NK008(nya)001:6671: bdud mo gar gyi dbang phyug ma //
NK008(nya)001:6672: dur khrod chen po'i gnas mchog nas //
NK008(nya)001:6674: dam tshig dbang gis gshegs su gsol //

NK008(nya)001:6677: tshangs pa'i rgyal po srin po'i gtso //
NK008(nya)001:6678: srog bdag g.yu yi smin ma can //
NK008(nya)001:6679: tshangs ba dung gi thor tshugs can //

NK008(nya)001:6686: tri se lag ring gshin rje'i gtso //
NK008(nya)001:6687: nag po lcags kyi ral pa can //
NK008(nya)001:6688: gshin rje'i ging phran 'khor dang bcas //
NK008(nya)001:6689: dur khrod chen po'i gnas mchog nas //

NK008(nya)001:6708: dam nyams dgra bgegs sgrol mdzad pa'i //
NK008(nya)001:6709: sgrol ging dam can sa ma ya //
NK008(nya)001:6710: dur khrod chen po'i gnas mchog nas //
NK008(nya)001:6712: dam tshig dbang gis gshegs su gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6713: rdo rje legs pa phyi 'khor sum brgya drug cu dang /
NK008(nya)001:6714: gri thogs ging chen bco brgyad dang //
NK008(nya)001:6715: khram thogs bdud po bcu drug dang //
NK008(nya)001:6716: zhags thogs mtshan chen bcu gnyis dang //
NK008(nya)001:6717: nad gtong ma mo bye ba'i tshogs //
NK008(nya)001:6718: dur khrod chen po'i gnas mchog nas //
NK008(nya)001:6720: dam tshig dbang gis gshegs su gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6721: dzahh+aa ba hoh badz+ra ma ya /
NK008(nya)001:6722: dkyil 'khor chen po'i pho brang dbus //
NK008(nya)001:6724: zhing chen bsnol ba'i khri stengs su //
NK008(nya)001:6725: dar dang za 'og gdan stengs su //
NK008(nya)001:6726: ma ru rtse yi lha tshogs rnams //
NK008(nya)001:6727: rim bzhin brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6728: ging ka ra sa ma ya tish+tha lhan /
NK008(nya)001:6730: bdag ni rnal 'byor dam tshig can //
NK008(nya)001:6731: khyod ni gsang ba'i sgrol ging tshogs //
NK008(nya)001:6732: mi 'da' ba yi phyag rgya dang //
NK008(nya)001:6733: dam tshig gzhung gis phyag 'tshal lo //
NK008(nya)001:6734: a ti p+au hoh pra t+aits+tsha hoh h'u /
NK008(nya)001:6735: rang byung gdod nas dag pa ste //
NK008(nya)001:6736: rtsa brgyad stong la sbyar ba'i sman //
NK008(nya)001:6737: ra sa ya na la sogs sman //
NK008(nya)001:6738: dug lnga sel ba'i bdud rtsi'i mchog /
NK008(nya)001:6740: bla ma brgyud pa thams cad dang //
NK008(nya)001:6741: yi dam lha tshogs 'khor bcas la //
NK008(nya)001:6742: dam rdzas bdud rtsi'i mchod pa 'bul //
NK008(nya)001:6743: bstan pa bsrung phyir bzhes su gsol //

NK008(nya)001:6757: bstan pa bsrung phyir bzhes su gsol //

NK008(nya)001:6762: bstan pa bsrung phyir bzhes su gsol //

NK008(nya)001:6780: bstan pa bsrung phyir bzhes su gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6781: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK008(nya)001:6783: sngon gyi bskal pa'i dang po la //
NK008(nya)001:6784: phyag na rdo rje'i spyan snga ru //
NK008(nya)001:6785: gsang ba'i sgrol ging khyed rnams kyis //
NK008(nya)001:6786: bstan pa bsrung bar khas blangs shing //
NK008(nya)001:6787: srog gi snying po dngos su phul //
NK008(nya)001:6788: rdo rje sgrol ging mtshan btags pa //
NK008(nya)001:6789: mi bsnyel phyir du rdo rje gtad //
NK008(nya)001:6790: dam tshig mchog las ma 'da' zhig /
NK008(nya)001:6791: ging ka ra sa ma ya h'u //
NK008(nya)001:6793: nga ni phyag na rdo rje ste //
NK008(nya)001:6794: khyod ni gsang ba'i sgrol ging ste //
NK008(nya)001:6795: dam tshig gnyan po bsre byed pa'i //
NK008(nya)001:6797: 'chi ba med pa'i bdud rtsi'i chu //
NK008(nya)001:6798: dam tshig snying gi khrag chen po //
NK008(nya)001:6799: gal te dam tshig bka' 'das na //
NK008(nya)001:6800: lus ngag thal bar gyur ta re //
NK008(nya)001:6802: bdag kyang lha ru khyod mchod cing //
NK008(nya)001:6803: khyod kyang dam las ma 'da' na ra kan //
NK008(nya)001:6805: srog dang srid la mnga' ma mdzad //
NK008(nya)001:6806: nga yang dam las mi 'da' zhing //
NK008(nya)001:6807: khyed kyang dam las ma 'da' zhig /
NK008(nya)001:6808: ci bcol byed par dam chos shig /
NK008(nya)001:6809: sa ma ya na ra kan /
NK008(nya)001:6810: ma h+aa rak+ta man+da la h'u /
NK008(nya)001:6812: phyi mchod nang mchod gsang mchod las //
NK008(nya)001:6815: ra dmar khrag chang sbyar ba'i mchod yon dang //
NK008(nya)001:6816: dbang po'i me tog sha chen dud pa'i sprin //
NK008(nya)001:6817: zhun chen mar me mkhris pa'i dri chab dang //
NK008(nya)001:6818: dgra sha khrag gi rgyun ldan zhal zas dang //
NK008(nya)001:6819: thod rnga rkang gling gsang ba'i rol mo bcas //
NK008(nya)001:6820: phyi nang 'dod yon lnga dang rin chen bdun //
NK008(nya)001:6821: lcags kyu lnga dang sgron ma lnga sbyar ba'i //
NK008(nya)001:6822: gser skyems gtsang ma phud kyi nang mchod dang //
NK008(nya)001:6823: btsan bshos dkar dmar bswe yi ra skyes sogs //
NK008(nya)001:6824: phyi nang gsang ba'i spyan gzigs dam rdzas tshogs //
NK008(nya)001:6825: dngos bshams yid kyis sprul pa'i mchod sprin 'di //
NK008(nya)001:6826: sgrool ging dmar po 'khor dang bcas la 'bul //
NK008(nya)001:6827: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrung phyir bzhes su gsol //
NK008(nya)001:6829: skyes bu ging chen 'khor bcas la //
NK008(nya)001:6830: phyi yi mchod pa 'bul ba ni //
NK008(nya)001:6831: mang yul stod kyi sman dang spos //
NK008(nya)001:6832: mon yul dbus kyi rtsod dang zhun //
NK008(nya)001:6833: lho brag stod kyi ras dang rdzas //
NK008(nya)001:6834: rgya yul mthil gyi dar dang zab //
